-- Adding all the Sequences and Triggers and Indexes to the end that Oracle SQL Developer Data Modeler 
-- does not create: 
    
COMMIT;



CREATE SEQUENCE BCHS_BCH_ID_SEQ MINVALUE 1 MAXVALUE 999999999999999999999999999 INCREMENT BY 1 START WITH 1 CYCLE;
CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER BCHS_BCH_ID_TRG 
   BEFORE INSERT ON BCHS 
      FOR EACH ROW 
         BEGIN 
            IF (:NEW.BCH_ID is null OR :NEW.BCH_ID = 0) THEN
               SELECT BCHS_BCH_ID_SEQ.nextval INTO :NEW.BCH_ID FROM DUAL; 
            END IF;
            SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.BCHSTARTTIME FROM DUAL;
            SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.BCHMODIFYTIME FROM DUAL;
         END BCHS_BCH_ID_TRG;
/

CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER BCHS_BEFOREUPD_TRG 
   BEFORE UPDATE ON BCHS
      FOR EACH ROW 
         BEGIN 
            IF (:NEW.BCHSTATUS=999 AND (:OLD.BCHSTATUS IS NULL OR :OLD.BCHSTATUS<>:NEW.BCHSTATUS)) THEN 
               SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.BCHENDTIME FROM DUAL;
               UPDATE BCHS_RCPS SET BCHS_RCPS.BCHRCPSTATUS=:NEW.BCHSTATUS,BCHS_RCPS.BCHRCPPROCTIME=TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') WHERE BCHS_RCPS.BCH_ID=:NEW.BCH_ID;
            ELSIF ((MOD(:NEW.BCHSTATUS,100)>=40 AND MOD(:NEW.BCHSTATUS,100)<=49 AND (:OLD.BCHSTATUS IS NULL OR :OLD.BCHSTATUS<>:NEW.BCHSTATUS)) OR  
                   (:NEW.BCHPUBERRARC<>:OLD.BCHPUBERRARC AND :NEW.BCHPUBERRARC>0 AND :NEW.BCHPUBERRARC IS NOT NULL) OR 
                   (:NEW.BCHPUBERRDST<>:OLD.BCHPUBERRDST AND :NEW.BCHPUBERRDST>0 AND :NEW.BCHPUBERRDST IS NOT NULL) OR 
                   (:NEW.BCHPUBERRNTF<>:OLD.BCHPUBERRNTF AND :NEW.BCHPUBERRNTF>0 AND :NEW.BCHPUBERRNTF IS NOT NULL)) THEN 
               SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.BCHERRTIME FROM DUAL;
               UPDATE BCHS_RCPS SET BCHS_RCPS.BCHRCPSTATUS=:NEW.BCHSTATUS,BCHS_RCPS.BCHRCPERRTIME=TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') WHERE BCHS_RCPS.BCH_ID=:NEW.BCH_ID;
            ELSIF (:NEW.BCHSTATUS IS NOT NULL AND (:NEW.BCHSTATUS < 415  OR :NEW.BCHSTATUS > 421) AND (:OLD.BCHSTATUS IS NULL OR :OLD.BCHSTATUS<>:NEW.BCHSTATUS)) THEN 
               UPDATE BCHS_RCPS SET BCHS_RCPS.BCHRCPSTATUS=:NEW.BCHSTATUS WHERE BCHS_RCPS.BCH_ID=:NEW.BCH_ID;
            END IF;
            SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.BCHMODIFYTIME FROM DUAL;
         END BCHS_BEFOREUPD_TRG;
/

CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER BCHSHIST_INS_TRG
   BEFORE DELETE ON BCHS
      FOR EACH ROW WHEN (OLD.BCHHISTORY = 1) 
         BEGIN
            Insert into BCHSHIST (
                BCH_ID,BCHNAME,BCHUNIQUE_ID,BCHSTARTINGTIME,BCHSTATUS,
                BCHSEQ,BCHTYPE,BCHBATCHNAME,BCHBATCHTYPE,BCHBY,
                BCHSELECTRULE,BCHPRTTYPE,BCHPRTTYPERULE,BCHSORTRULE,
                BCHSTARTTIME,BCHERRTIME,BCHENDTIME,BCHTRNCOUNT,BCHRCPCOUNT,BCHPAGECOUNT,BCHSHEETCOUNT,BCHWEIGHT,
                BCHBREAKTYPE,BCHBREAKVALUE,
                BCHARCHIVE,BCHARCDEST,BCHPUBTOTALARC,BCHPUBERRARC,BCHPUBPROCARC,
                BCHSIGNING,BCHSGNDEST,BCHSGNTMPL,BCHPUBTOTALSGN,BCHPUBERRSGN,BCHPUBPROCSGN,
                BCHPUBLISH,BCHMIMETYPE,BCHPRTLOGNAME,
                BCHPUBEMAIL,BCHPUBEMAILRULE,BCHPUBLANGRULE,BCHPUBMSGTYPRULE,BCHPUBTOTALDST,BCHPUBERRDST,BCHPUBPROCDST,
                BCHENABLENTF,BCHNTFRULE,BCHLANGRULE,BCHNTFMSGTYPRULE,BCHPUBTOTALNTF,BCHPUBERRNTF,BCHPUBPROCNTF,BCHERR_ID,
                CALLBACK,BATCHBANNERBEGINSCRIPT,BATCHBANNERENDSCRIPT,
                BATCHBANNERBEGINFORM,BATCHBANNERENDFORM,
                TRANSBANNERBEGINSCRIPT,TRANSBANNERENDSCRIPT,
                TRANSBANNERBEGINFORM,TRANSBANNERENDFORM,
                BCHAPPDATE001,BCHAPPDATE002,BCHAPPDATE003,BCHAPPDATE004,BCHAPPDATE005,
                BCHAPPDEC001,BCHAPPDEC002,BCHAPPDEC003,BCHAPPDEC004,BCHAPPDEC005,
                BCHAPPINT001,BCHAPPINT002,BCHAPPINT003,BCHAPPINT004,BCHAPPINT005,
                BCHAPPSTR001,BCHAPPSTR002,BCHAPPSTR003,BCHAPPSTR004,BCHAPPSTR005,
                BCHAPPSTR006,BCHAPPSTR007,BCHAPPSTR008,BCHAPPSTR009,BCHAPPSTR010,
                BCHCUSDATE001,BCHCUSDATE002,BCHCUSDATE003,BCHCUSDATE004,BCHCUSDATE005,
                BCHCUSDEC001,BCHCUSDEC002,BCHCUSDEC003,BCHCUSDEC004,BCHCUSDEC005,
                BCHCUSINT001,BCHCUSINT002,BCHCUSINT003,BCHCUSINT004,BCHCUSINT005,
                BCHCUSSTR001,BCHCUSSTR002,BCHCUSSTR003,BCHCUSSTR004,BCHCUSSTR005,
                BCHCUSSTR006,BCHCUSSTR007,BCHCUSSTR008,BCHCUSSTR009,BCHCUSSTR010,
                BCHRETENTION,BCHRETHOLD,BCHMODIFYTIME,BCHHISTORY
        ) VALUES (
                :OLD.BCH_ID,:OLD.BCHNAME,:OLD.BCHUNIQUE_ID,:OLD.BCHSTARTINGTIME,:OLD.BCHSTATUS,
                :OLD.BCHSEQ,:OLD.BCHTYPE,:OLD.BCHBATCHNAME,:OLD.BCHBATCHTYPE,:OLD.BCHBY,
                :OLD.BCHSELECTRULE,:OLD.BCHPRTTYPE,:OLD.BCHPRTTYPERULE,:OLD.BCHSORTRULE,
                :OLD.BCHSTARTTIME,:OLD.BCHERRTIME,:OLD.BCHENDTIME,:OLD.BCHTRNCOUNT,:OLD.BCHRCPCOUNT,:OLD.BCHPAGECOUNT,:OLD.BCHSHEETCOUNT,:OLD.BCHWEIGHT,
                :OLD.BCHBREAKTYPE,:OLD.BCHBREAKVALUE,
                :OLD.BCHARCHIVE,:OLD.BCHARCDEST,:OLD.BCHPUBTOTALARC,:OLD.BCHPUBERRARC,:OLD.BCHPUBPROCARC,
                :OLD.BCHSIGNING,:OLD.BCHSGNDEST,:OLD.BCHSGNTMPL,:OLD.BCHPUBTOTALSGN,:OLD.BCHPUBERRSGN,:OLD.BCHPUBPROCSGN,
                :OLD.BCHPUBLISH,:OLD.BCHMIMETYPE,:OLD.BCHPRTLOGNAME,
                :OLD.BCHPUBEMAIL,:OLD.BCHPUBEMAILRULE,:OLD.BCHPUBLANGRULE,:OLD.BCHPUBMSGTYPRULE,:OLD.BCHPUBTOTALDST,:OLD.BCHPUBERRDST,:OLD.BCHPUBPROCDST,
                :OLD.BCHENABLENTF,:OLD.BCHNTFRULE,:OLD.BCHLANGRULE,:OLD.BCHNTFMSGTYPRULE,:OLD.BCHPUBTOTALNTF,:OLD.BCHPUBERRNTF,:OLD.BCHPUBPROCNTF,:OLD.BCHERR_ID,
                :OLD.CALLBACK,:OLD.BATCHBANNERBEGINSCRIPT,:OLD.BATCHBANNERENDSCRIPT,
                :OLD.BATCHBANNERBEGINFORM,:OLD.BATCHBANNERENDFORM,
                :OLD.TRANSBANNERBEGINSCRIPT,:OLD.TRANSBANNERENDSCRIPT,
                :OLD.TRANSBANNERBEGINFORM,:OLD.TRANSBANNERENDFORM,
                :OLD.BCHAPPDATE001,:OLD.BCHAPPDATE002,:OLD.BCHAPPDATE003,:OLD.BCHAPPDATE004,:OLD.BCHAPPDATE005,
                :OLD.BCHAPPDEC001,:OLD.BCHAPPDEC002,:OLD.BCHAPPDEC003,:OLD.BCHAPPDEC004,:OLD.BCHAPPDEC005,
                :OLD.BCHAPPINT001,:OLD.BCHAPPINT002,:OLD.BCHAPPINT003,:OLD.BCHAPPINT004,:OLD.BCHAPPINT005,
                :OLD.BCHAPPSTR001,:OLD.BCHAPPSTR002,:OLD.BCHAPPSTR003,:OLD.BCHAPPSTR004,:OLD.BCHAPPSTR005,
                :OLD.BCHAPPSTR006,:OLD.BCHAPPSTR007,:OLD.BCHAPPSTR008,:OLD.BCHAPPSTR009,:OLD.BCHAPPSTR010,
                :OLD.BCHCUSDATE001,:OLD.BCHCUSDATE002,:OLD.BCHCUSDATE003,:OLD.BCHCUSDATE004,:OLD.BCHCUSDATE005,
                :OLD.BCHCUSDEC001,:OLD.BCHCUSDEC002,:OLD.BCHCUSDEC003,:OLD.BCHCUSDEC004,:OLD.BCHCUSDEC005,
                :OLD.BCHCUSINT001,:OLD.BCHCUSINT002,:OLD.BCHCUSINT003,:OLD.BCHCUSINT004,:OLD.BCHCUSINT005,
                :OLD.BCHCUSSTR001,:OLD.BCHCUSSTR002,:OLD.BCHCUSSTR003,:OLD.BCHCUSSTR004,:OLD.BCHCUSSTR005,
                :OLD.BCHCUSSTR006,:OLD.BCHCUSSTR007,:OLD.BCHCUSSTR008,:OLD.BCHCUSSTR009,:OLD.BCHCUSSTR010,
                :OLD.BCHRETENTION,:OLD.BCHRETHOLD,:OLD.BCHMODIFYTIME,:OLD.BCHHISTORY
            ) ;
         END BCHSHIST_INS_TRG;
/


CREATE SEQUENCE ERRS_ERR_ID_SEQ MINVALUE 1 MAXVALUE 999999999999999999999999999 INCREMENT BY 1 START WITH 1 CYCLE;
CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER ERRS_ERR_ID_TRG 
   BEFORE INSERT ON ERRS 
      FOR EACH ROW 
         BEGIN 
            IF (:NEW.ERR_ID is null OR :NEW.ERR_ID = 0) THEN
               SELECT ERRS_ERR_ID_SEQ.nextval INTO :NEW.ERR_ID FROM DUAL; 
            END IF;
            SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.ERRTIME FROM DUAL;
         END ERRS_ERR_ID_TRG;
/

CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER ERRS_AFTERINSERT_TRG 
   AFTER INSERT ON ERRS 
      FOR EACH ROW
         BEGIN
            UPDATE JOBS SET JOBERR_ID=:NEW.ERR_ID WHERE JOBS.JOB_ID=:NEW.JOB_ID AND (JOBERR_ID=0 OR JOBERR_ID IS NULL); 
            UPDATE TRNS SET TRNERR_ID=:NEW.ERR_ID,TRNS.TRNDOLOG=1 WHERE TRNS.TRN_ID=:NEW.TRN_ID AND (TRNERR_ID=0 OR TRNERR_ID IS NULL);
            UPDATE RCPS SET RCPERR_ID=:NEW.ERR_ID WHERE RCPS.RCP_ID=:NEW.RCP_ID AND (RCPERR_ID=0 OR RCPERR_ID IS NULL);
            UPDATE BCHS SET BCHERR_ID=:NEW.ERR_ID WHERE BCHS.BCH_ID=:NEW.BCH_ID AND (BCHERR_ID=0 OR BCHERR_ID IS NULL);
            UPDATE PUBS SET PUBERR_ID=:NEW.ERR_ID WHERE PUBS.PUB_ID=:NEW.PUB_ID AND (PUBERR_ID=0 OR PUBERR_ID IS NULL);
         END ERRS_AFTERINSERT_TRG;
/

CREATE SEQUENCE JOBS_JOB_ID_SEQ MINVALUE 1 MAXVALUE 999999999999999999999999999 INCREMENT BY 1 START WITH 1 CYCLE;
CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER JOBS_JOB_ID_TRG 
   BEFORE INSERT ON JOBS 
      FOR EACH ROW 
         BEGIN 
            IF (:NEW.JOB_ID is null OR :NEW.JOB_ID = 0) THEN
               SELECT JOBS_JOB_ID_SEQ.nextval INTO :NEW.JOB_ID FROM DUAL; 
            END IF;
            SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.JOBSTARTTIME FROM DUAL;
         END JOBS_JOB_ID_TRG;
/

CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER JOBS_BEFOREUPD_TRG 
   BEFORE UPDATE ON JOBS
      FOR EACH ROW  
         BEGIN 
            IF (:NEW.JOBSTATUS<>:OLD.JOBSTATUS AND 
                (:NEW.JOBSTATUS IS NOT NULL AND (MOD(:NEW.JOBSTATUS,100)>=40 AND MOD(:NEW.JOBSTATUS,100)<=49)) AND
                (:OLD.JOBSTATUS IS NULL OR (:OLD.JOBSTATUS IS NOT NULL AND (MOD(:OLD.JOBSTATUS,100)<40 OR MOD(:OLD.JOBSTATUS,100)>49)))) THEN 
               :NEW.JOBSTATUS:=:NEW.JOBSTATUS;
            ELSIF (:NEW.JOBBCHERR>:OLD.JOBBCHERR AND :NEW.JOBBCHERR>0 AND (MOD(:NEW.JOBSTATUS,100)<40 OR MOD(:NEW.JOBSTATUS,100)>49)) THEN 
               :NEW.JOBSTATUS:=441;
            ELSIF (:NEW.JOBRCPERR>:OLD.JOBRCPERR AND :NEW.JOBRCPERR>0 AND (MOD(:NEW.JOBSTATUS,100)<40 OR MOD(:NEW.JOBSTATUS,100)>49)) THEN 
               :NEW.JOBSTATUS:=341;
            ELSIF (:NEW.JOBTRNERR>:OLD.JOBTRNERR AND :NEW.JOBTRNERR>0 AND (MOD(:NEW.JOBSTATUS,100)<40 OR MOD(:NEW.JOBSTATUS,100)>49)) THEN 
               :NEW.JOBSTATUS:=241;
            ELSIF (:NEW.JOBTRNWIP>:OLD.JOBTRNWIP AND :NEW.JOBTRNWIP>0 AND :NEW.JOBSTATUS<290 AND (MOD(:NEW.JOBSTATUS,100)<40 OR MOD(:NEW.JOBSTATUS,100)>49)) THEN 
               :NEW.JOBSTATUS:=290;
            ELSIF (:NEW.JOBTRNTOTAL=(:NEW.JOBTRNPROC+:NEW.JOBTRNWIP) AND :NEW.JOBTRNTOTAL>0 AND :NEW.JOBTRNWIP>0) THEN 
            	 :NEW.JOBTRNSCH:=0; 
            	 :NEW.JOBSTATUS:=290;
            ELSIF (:OLD.JOBRCPTOTAL<1 AND :NEW.JOBRCPTOTAL>0 AND :NEW.JOBSTATUS<300 AND (MOD(:NEW.JOBSTATUS,100)<40 OR MOD(:NEW.JOBSTATUS,100)>49) AND :NEW.JOBTRNWIP<1) THEN 
               :NEW.JOBSTATUS:=311;
            ELSIF (:OLD.JOBBCHTOTAL<1 AND :NEW.JOBBCHTOTAL>0 AND :NEW.JOBSTATUS<400 AND (MOD(:NEW.JOBSTATUS,100)<40 OR MOD(:NEW.JOBSTATUS,100)>49) AND :NEW.JOBTRNWIP<1) THEN 
               :NEW.JOBSTATUS:=411;
            END IF;

            IF (:NEW.JOBBCHTOTAL=:NEW.JOBBCHPROC AND :NEW.JOBBCHTOTAL>0 AND
                :NEW.JOBRCPTOTAL=:NEW.JOBRCPPROC AND :NEW.JOBRCPTOTAL>0 AND
                :NEW.JOBTRNTOTAL=:NEW.JOBTRNPROC AND :NEW.JOBTRNTOTAL>0 AND
                 (:NEW.JOBBCHPROC<>:OLD.JOBBCHPROC OR 
                  :NEW.JOBRCPPROC<>:OLD.JOBRCPPROC OR  
                  :NEW.JOBTRNPROC<>:OLD.JOBTRNPROC ) AND 
                :NEW.JOBSTATUS<900 AND :NEW.JOBSTATUS>0) THEN 
               :NEW.JOBSTATUS:=999;
            END IF;
            
            IF (:OLD.JOBSTATUS<>416 AND 
                :NEW.JOBTRNTOTAL<>0 AND
                :NEW.JOBTRNSCH<>0 AND
                :NEW.JOBTRNERR=0 AND
                :NEW.JOBTRNTOTAL=(:NEW.JOBTRNPROC+:NEW.JOBTRNSCH)) THEN
                :NEW.JOBSTATUS:=416;
            END IF;
            
            IF (:NEW.JOBBCHTOTAL=:NEW.JOBBCHPROC AND :NEW.JOBBCHTOTAL>0) THEN
               SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.JOBBCHENDTIME FROM DUAL;
               :NEW.JOBBCHSCH:=0;
            END IF;
            IF (:NEW.JOBRCPTOTAL=:NEW.JOBRCPPROC AND :NEW.JOBRCPTOTAL>0) THEN
               SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.JOBRCPENDTIME FROM DUAL;
               :NEW.JOBRCPSCH:=0;
            END IF; 
            IF (:NEW.JOBTRNTOTAL=:NEW.JOBTRNPROC AND :NEW.JOBTRNTOTAL>0) THEN
               SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.JOBTRNENDTIME FROM DUAL;
               :NEW.JOBTRNSCH:=0;
            END IF; 

            IF (:NEW.JOBSTATUS=111 AND :OLD.JOBSTATUS<>:NEW.JOBSTATUS AND :NEW.JOBSTARTTIME IS NULL) THEN
               SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.JOBSTARTTIME FROM DUAL;
            ELSIF (:NEW.JOBSTATUS=211 AND :OLD.JOBSTATUS<>:NEW.JOBSTATUS AND :NEW.JOBTRNSTARTTIME IS NULL) THEN
               SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.JOBTRNSTARTTIME FROM DUAL;
            ELSIF (:NEW.JOBSTATUS=311 AND :OLD.JOBSTATUS<>:NEW.JOBSTATUS AND :NEW.JOBRCPSTARTTIME IS NULL) THEN
               SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.JOBRCPSTARTTIME FROM DUAL;
            ELSIF (:NEW.JOBSTATUS=411 AND :OLD.JOBSTATUS<>:NEW.JOBSTATUS AND :NEW.JOBBCHSTARTTIME IS NULL) THEN
               SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.JOBBCHSTARTTIME FROM DUAL;
            ELSIF (:NEW.JOBSTATUS=999 AND :OLD.JOBSTATUS<>:NEW.JOBSTATUS AND :NEW.JOBENDTIME IS NULL) THEN
               IF (:NEW.JOBBCHENDTIME IS NULL) THEN 
                  SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.JOBBCHENDTIME FROM DUAL;
               END IF;
               IF (:NEW.JOBRCPENDTIME IS NULL) THEN 
                  SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.JOBRCPENDTIME FROM DUAL;
               END IF;
               IF (:NEW.JOBBCHENDTIME IS NULL) THEN 
                  SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.JOBBCHENDTIME FROM DUAL;
               END IF;
               SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.JOBENDTIME FROM DUAL;
            END IF;
            IF (:NEW.JOBREPLYSENT=1 AND :NEW.JOBREPLYSENT<>:OLD.JOBREPLYSENT) THEN
            		SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.JOBREPLYSENTTIME FROM DUAL;	
            END IF;
         END JOBS_BEFOREUPD_TRG;
/

CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER JOBSHIST_INS_TRG
   BEFORE DELETE ON JOBS
      FOR EACH ROW WHEN (OLD.JOBHISTORY = 1) 
         BEGIN
            Insert into JOBSHIST (
                JOB_ID,JOBNAME,JOBPRIORITY,JOBSTATUS,JOBUNIQUE_ID,
                JOBPRTLOGNAME,JOBPAYLOADTYPE,JOBPAYLOADREF,JOBPAYLOADBLOB,JOBPAYLOADXML,
                JOBATTACHMENTS,JOBSTARTTIME,JOBENDTIME,JOBERR_ID,
                JOBTRNTOTAL,JOBTRNWIP,JOBTRNERR,JOBTRNSCH,JOBTRNPROC,JOBTRNSTARTTIME,JOBTRNENDTIME,
                JOBRCPTOTAL,JOBRCPERR,JOBRCPSCH,JOBRCPPROC,JOBRCPSTARTTIME,JOBRCPENDTIME,
                JOBBCHTOTAL,JOBBCHERR,JOBBCHSCH,JOBBCHPROC,JOBBCHSTARTTIME,JOBBCHENDTIME,
                JOBRETENTION,JOBRETHOLD,JOBHISTORY,JOBREPLYTOURI,JOBREPLYSENT,JOBREPLYSENTTIME
        ) VALUES (
                :OLD.JOB_ID,:OLD.JOBNAME,:OLD.JOBPRIORITY,:OLD.JOBSTATUS,:OLD.JOBUNIQUE_ID,
                :OLD.JOBPRTLOGNAME,:OLD.JOBPAYLOADTYPE,:OLD.JOBPAYLOADREF,:OLD.JOBPAYLOADBLOB,:OLD.JOBPAYLOADXML,
                :OLD.JOBATTACHMENTS,:OLD.JOBSTARTTIME,:OLD.JOBENDTIME,:OLD.JOBERR_ID,
                :OLD.JOBTRNTOTAL,:OLD.JOBTRNWIP,:OLD.JOBTRNERR,:OLD.JOBTRNSCH,:OLD.JOBTRNPROC,:OLD.JOBTRNSTARTTIME,:OLD.JOBTRNENDTIME,
                :OLD.JOBRCPTOTAL,:OLD.JOBRCPERR,:OLD.JOBRCPSCH,:OLD.JOBRCPPROC,:OLD.JOBRCPSTARTTIME,:OLD.JOBRCPENDTIME,
                :OLD.JOBBCHTOTAL,:OLD.JOBBCHERR,:OLD.JOBBCHSCH,:OLD.JOBBCHPROC,:OLD.JOBBCHSTARTTIME,:OLD.JOBBCHENDTIME,
                :OLD.JOBRETENTION,:OLD.JOBRETHOLD,:OLD.JOBHISTORY,:OLD.JOBREPLYTOURI,:OLD.JOBREPLYSENT,:OLD.JOBREPLYSENTTIME

        ) ;
         END JOBSHIST_INS_TRG;
/


CREATE SEQUENCE LOGS_LOG_ID_SEQ MINVALUE 1 MAXVALUE 999999999999999999999999999 INCREMENT BY 1 START WITH 1 CYCLE;
CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER LOGS_LOG_ID_TRG 
   BEFORE INSERT ON LOGS 
      FOR EACH ROW 
         BEGIN 
            IF (:NEW.LOG_ID is null OR :NEW.LOG_ID = 0) THEN
               SELECT LOGS_LOG_ID_SEQ.nextval INTO :NEW.LOG_ID FROM DUAL; 
            END IF;
            SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.LOGTIME FROM DUAL;
         END LOGS_LOG_ID_TRG;
/



CREATE SEQUENCE RCPS_RCP_ID_SEQ MINVALUE 1 MAXVALUE 999999999999999999999999999 INCREMENT BY 1 START WITH 1 CYCLE;
CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER RCPS_RCP_ID_TRG 
   BEFORE INSERT ON RCPS 
      FOR EACH ROW 
         BEGIN 
            IF (:NEW.RCP_ID is null OR :NEW.RCP_ID = 0) THEN
               SELECT RCPS_RCP_ID_SEQ.nextval INTO :NEW.RCP_ID FROM DUAL; 
            END IF;
            SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.RCPSTARTTIME FROM DUAL;
         END RCPS_RCP_ID_TRG;
/

CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER RCPSHIST_INS_TRG
   BEFORE DELETE ON RCPS
      FOR EACH ROW 
      BEGIN
         IF(:OLD.RCPHISTORY=0) THEN
            UPDATE TRNS SET TRNS.TRNRCPTOTAL=TRNS.TRNRCPTOTAL-1,TRNS.TRNDOLOG=0 WHERE TRNS.TRN_ID=:OLD.TRN_ID;
         ELSE
            Insert into RCPSHIST (
                RCP_ID,TRN_ID,RCPUNIQUE_ID,BATCHNAME,BATCHTYPE,RCPSTATUS,
                RCPBCHTOTAL,RCPBCHERR,RCPBCHSCH,RCPBCHPROC,
                RCPDATATYPE,RCPOUTTYPE,RCPOUTBLOB,RCPOUTREF,RCPOUTSIZE,
                RCPSTARTTIME,RCPENDTIME,RCPPAGECOUNT,RCPSHEETCOUNT,RCPWEIGHT,
                RCPTRAY1,RCPTRAY2,RCPTRAY3,RCPTRAY4,RCPTRAY5,RCPTRAY6,RCPTRAY7,RCPTRAY8,RCPTRAY9,
                ADR_INDEX,ADR_CODE,ADR_NAME,ADR_ADDRESS1,ADR_ADDRESS2,ADR_CITY,ADR_STATE,
                ADR_COUNTRY,ADR_POSTALCODE,ADR_EMAIL,ADR_ENCLOSURES,ADR_FAX,ADR_PHONE,ADR_HOMEPHONE,
                ADR_SELECTED,ADR_PREFERRED,ADR_RFU,ADR_ROLE,ADR_SIGNINGROLE,ADR_TRACKING,ADR_TYPE,ADR_LANGUAGE,ADR_HOUSEHOLD,
                RCPERR_ID,
                RCPAPPDATE001,RCPAPPDATE002,RCPAPPDATE003,RCPAPPDATE004,RCPAPPDATE005,
                RCPAPPDEC001,RCPAPPDEC002,RCPAPPDEC003,RCPAPPDEC004,RCPAPPDEC005,
                RCPAPPINT001,RCPAPPINT002,RCPAPPINT003,RCPAPPINT004,RCPAPPINT005,
                RCPAPPSTR001,RCPAPPSTR002,RCPAPPSTR003,RCPAPPSTR004,RCPAPPSTR005,
                RCPAPPSTR006,RCPAPPSTR007,RCPAPPSTR008,RCPAPPSTR009,RCPAPPSTR010,
                RCPAPPSTR011,RCPAPPSTR012,RCPAPPSTR013,RCPAPPSTR014,RCPAPPSTR015,
                RCPCUSDATE001,RCPCUSDATE002,RCPCUSDATE003,RCPCUSDATE004,RCPCUSDATE005,
                RCPCUSDEC001,RCPCUSDEC002,RCPCUSDEC003,RCPCUSDEC004,RCPCUSDEC005,
                RCPCUSINT001,RCPCUSINT002,RCPCUSINT003,RCPCUSINT004,RCPCUSINT005,
                RCPCUSSTR001,RCPCUSSTR002,RCPCUSSTR003,RCPCUSSTR004,RCPCUSSTR005,
                RCPCUSSTR006,RCPCUSSTR007,RCPCUSSTR008,RCPCUSSTR009,RCPCUSSTR010,
                RCPCUSSTR011,RCPCUSSTR012,RCPCUSSTR013,RCPCUSSTR014,RCPCUSSTR015,
                RCBPRTFLAG,RCBRCPCODE,RCBRCPNAME,RCBERROR,RCPHISTORY
            ) VALUES (
                :OLD.RCP_ID,:OLD.TRN_ID,:OLD.RCPUNIQUE_ID,:OLD.BATCHNAME,:OLD.BATCHTYPE,:OLD.RCPSTATUS,
                :OLD.RCPBCHTOTAL,:OLD.RCPBCHERR,:OLD.RCPBCHSCH,:OLD.RCPBCHPROC,
                :OLD.RCPDATATYPE,:OLD.RCPOUTTYPE,:OLD.RCPOUTBLOB,:OLD.RCPOUTREF,:OLD.RCPOUTSIZE,
                :OLD.RCPSTARTTIME,:OLD.RCPENDTIME,:OLD.RCPPAGECOUNT,:OLD.RCPSHEETCOUNT,:OLD.RCPWEIGHT,
                :OLD.RCPTRAY1,:OLD.RCPTRAY2,:OLD.RCPTRAY3,:OLD.RCPTRAY4,:OLD.RCPTRAY5,:OLD.RCPTRAY6,:OLD.RCPTRAY7,:OLD.RCPTRAY8,:OLD.RCPTRAY9,
                :OLD.ADR_INDEX,:OLD.ADR_CODE,:OLD.ADR_NAME,:OLD.ADR_ADDRESS1,:OLD.ADR_ADDRESS2,:OLD.ADR_CITY,:OLD.ADR_STATE,
                :OLD.ADR_COUNTRY,:OLD.ADR_POSTALCODE,:OLD.ADR_EMAIL,:OLD.ADR_ENCLOSURES,:OLD.ADR_FAX,:OLD.ADR_PHONE,:OLD.ADR_HOMEPHONE,

                :OLD.RCPERR_ID,
                :OLD.RCPAPPDATE001,:OLD.RCPAPPDATE002,:OLD.RCPAPPDATE003,:OLD.RCPAPPDATE004,:OLD.RCPAPPDATE005,
                :OLD.RCPAPPDEC001,:OLD.RCPAPPDEC002,:OLD.RCPAPPDEC003,:OLD.RCPAPPDEC004,:OLD.RCPAPPDEC005,
                :OLD.RCPAPPINT001,:OLD.RCPAPPINT002,:OLD.RCPAPPINT003,:OLD.RCPAPPINT004,:OLD.RCPAPPINT005,

                :OLD.RCPCUSDEC001,:OLD.RCPCUSDEC002,:OLD.RCPCUSDEC003,:OLD.RCPCUSDEC004,:OLD.RCPCUSDEC005,
                :OLD.RCPCUSINT001,:OLD.RCPCUSINT002,:OLD.RCPCUSINT003,:OLD.RCPCUSINT004,:OLD.RCPCUSINT005,
                :OLD.RCPCUSSTR001,:OLD.RCPCUSSTR002,:OLD.RCPCUSSTR003,:OLD.RCPCUSSTR004,:OLD.RCPCUSSTR005,
                :OLD.RCPCUSSTR006,:OLD.RCPCUSSTR007,:OLD.RCPCUSSTR008,:OLD.RCPCUSSTR009,:OLD.RCPCUSSTR010,
                :OLD.RCPCUSSTR011,:OLD.RCPCUSSTR012,:OLD.RCPCUSSTR013,:OLD.RCPCUSSTR014,:OLD.RCPCUSSTR015,
                :OLD.RCBPRTFLAG,:OLD.RCBRCPCODE,:OLD.RCBRCPNAME,:OLD.RCBERROR,:OLD.RCPHISTORY
            ) ;
         END IF;
      END RCPSHIST_INS_TRG;
/


CREATE SEQUENCE TRNS_TRN_ID_SEQ MINVALUE 1 MAXVALUE 999999999999999999999999999 INCREMENT BY 1 START WITH 1 CYCLE;
CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER TRNS_TRN_ID_TRG 
   BEFORE INSERT ON TRNS 
      FOR EACH ROW 
         BEGIN 
            IF (:NEW.TRN_ID is null OR :NEW.TRN_ID = 0) THEN
               SELECT TRNS_TRN_ID_SEQ.nextval INTO :NEW.TRN_ID FROM DUAL; 
            END IF;
	    IF(:NEW.TRNDOLOG>1) THEN 
               :NEW.TRNAPPINT001:=:NEW.TRNAPPINT001+1; 
            END IF ;
            SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.CREATETIME FROM DUAL;
            SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.MODIFYTIME FROM DUAL;
            SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.TRNMODIFYTIME FROM DUAL;
            SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.TRNSTARTTIME FROM DUAL;
            IF(:NEW.STATUSCODE='W' AND 
               (:NEW.APPROVALSTATE='10' OR :NEW.APPROVALSTATE='20' OR 
                :NEW.APPROVALSTATE='30' OR :NEW.APPROVALSTATE='40') AND   
              (:NEW.TRNSTATUS<290 OR :NEW.TRNSTATUS IS NULL)) THEN 
              :NEW.TRNSTATUS:=290; 
            END IF;
            IF(:NEW.STATUSCODE='W') THEN 
              UPDATE JOBS SET JOBS.JOBTRNWIP=JOBS.JOBTRNWIP+1 WHERE JOBS.JOB_ID=:NEW.JOB_ID;
            END IF;
         END TRNS_TRN_ID_TRG;
/


CREATE SEQUENCE TRNSLOG_TRNSLOG_ID_SEQ MINVALUE 1 MAXVALUE 999999999999999999999999999 INCREMENT BY 1 START WITH 1 CYCLE;
CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER TRNSLOG_TRNSLOG_ID_TRG 
   BEFORE INSERT ON TRNSLOG 
      FOR EACH ROW WHEN (NEW.TRNSLOG_ID is null OR NEW.TRNSLOG_ID = 0) 
         BEGIN SELECT TRNSLOG_TRNSLOG_ID_SEQ.nextval INTO :NEW.TRNSLOG_ID FROM DUAL; 
         END TRNSLOG_TRNSLOG_ID_TRG;
/

CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER TRNS_AFTERINS_TRG
   AFTER INSERT ON TRNS
     FOR EACH ROW WHEN (NEW.TRNDOLOG>0)
     BEGIN
       IF (:NEW.TRNDOLOG=1) THEN
         Insert into TRNSLOG (JOB_ID,TRN_ID,UNIQUE_ID,KEY1,KEY2,KEY3,KEYID,FORMSETID,
                ARCKEY,RECTYPE,DESCR,TRNNAME,DOCTYPE,DOCSUBTYPE,ORIGUSER,

                BEGINTIME,TRNSTARTTIME,
                MODIFYTIME,TRNMODIFYTIME,
                ARCTIME,RETENTION,TRNENDTIME,
                ENDTIME,JURISDICTN,LOCID,QUEUEID,SUBLOCID,AGENCYID,
                FROMUSER,FROMTIME,FROMGROUP,TOTIME,TOUSER,TOGROUP,
                ROUTEDESC,PROCESSNAME,
                TRNAPPDATE001,TRNAPPDATE002,TRNAPPDATE003,TRNAPPDATE004,TRNAPPDATE005,
                TRNAPPDEC001,TRNAPPDEC002,TRNAPPDEC003,TRNAPPDEC004,TRNAPPDEC005,
                TRNAPPINT001,TRNAPPINT002,TRNAPPINT003,TRNAPPINT004,TRNAPPINT005,
                TRNAPPSTR001,TRNAPPSTR002,TRNAPPSTR003,TRNAPPSTR004,TRNAPPSTR005,
                TRNAPPSTR006,TRNAPPSTR007,TRNAPPSTR008,TRNAPPSTR009,TRNAPPSTR010,
                TRNAPPSTR011,TRNAPPSTR012,TRNAPPSTR013,TRNAPPSTR014,TRNAPPSTR015,
                TRNCUSDATE001,TRNCUSDATE002,TRNCUSDATE003,TRNCUSDATE004,TRNCUSDATE005,
                TRNCUSDATE006,TRNCUSDATE007,TRNCUSDATE008,TRNCUSDATE009,TRNCUSDATE010,
                TRNCUSDATE011,TRNCUSDATE012,TRNCUSDATE013,TRNCUSDATE014,TRNCUSDATE015,
                TRNCUSDEC001,TRNCUSDEC002,TRNCUSDEC003,TRNCUSDEC004,TRNCUSDEC005,
                TRNCUSINT001,TRNCUSINT002,TRNCUSINT003,TRNCUSINT004,TRNCUSINT005,
                TRNCUSSTR001,TRNCUSSTR002,TRNCUSSTR003,TRNCUSSTR004,TRNCUSSTR005,
                TRNCUSSTR006,TRNCUSSTR007,TRNCUSSTR008,TRNCUSSTR009,TRNCUSSTR010,
                TRNCUSSTR011,TRNCUSSTR012,TRNCUSSTR013,TRNCUSSTR014,TRNCUSSTR015,
                TRNCUSSTR016,TRNCUSSTR017,TRNCUSSTR018,TRNCUSSTR019,TRNCUSSTR020,
                ACTION,REASON_ID,TRNSTATUS,TRNRCPTOTAL,TRNRCPERR,TRNRCPSCH,TRNRCPPROC,
                TRNBCHTOTAL,TRNBCHERR,TRNBCHSCH,TRNBCHPROC,

        ) VALUES (

                :NEW.ARCKEY,:NEW.RECTYPE,:NEW.DESCR,:NEW.TRNNAME,:NEW.DOCTYPE,:NEW.DOCSUBTYPE,:NEW.ORIGUSER,
                :NEW.CURRUSER,:NEW.CURRGROUP,:NEW.CURRROLE,:NEW.CURRSUPER,:NEW.CURRAPP_ID,:NEW.STATUSCODE,:NEW.TRANCODE,
                :NEW.APPROVALSTATE,:NEW.SECLEVEL,:NEW.TRNERR_ID,:NEW.INUSE,:NEW.CUSTOMIZED,:NEW.CREATETIME,
                :NEW.BEGINTIME,:NEW.TRNSTARTTIME,
                TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),
                TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),
                :NEW.ARCTIME,:NEW.RETENTION,:NEW.TRNENDTIME,
                :NEW.ENDTIME,:NEW.JURISDICTN,:NEW.LOCID,:NEW.QUEUEID,:NEW.SUBLOCID,:NEW.AGENCYID,
                :NEW.FROMUSER,:NEW.FROMTIME,:NEW.FROMGROUP,:NEW.TOTIME,:NEW.TOUSER,:NEW.TOGROUP,
                :NEW.ROUTEDESC,:NEW.PROCESSNAME,
                :NEW.TRNAPPDATE001,:NEW.TRNAPPDATE002,:NEW.TRNAPPDATE003,:NEW.TRNAPPDATE004,:NEW.TRNAPPDATE005,
                :NEW.TRNAPPDEC001,:NEW.TRNAPPDEC002,:NEW.TRNAPPDEC003,:NEW.TRNAPPDEC004,:NEW.TRNAPPDEC005,
                :NEW.TRNAPPINT001,:NEW.TRNAPPINT002,:NEW.TRNAPPINT003,:NEW.TRNAPPINT004,:NEW.TRNAPPINT005,
                :NEW.TRNAPPSTR001,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR002,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR003,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR004,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR005,
                :NEW.TRNAPPSTR006,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR007,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR008,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR009,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR010,
                :NEW.TRNAPPSTR011,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR012,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR013,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR014,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR015,
                :NEW.TRNCUSDATE001,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE002,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE003,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE004,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE005,
                :NEW.TRNCUSDATE006,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE007,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE008,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE009,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE010,
                :NEW.TRNCUSDATE011,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE012,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE013,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE014,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE015,
                :NEW.TRNCUSDEC001,:NEW.TRNCUSDEC002,:NEW.TRNCUSDEC003,:NEW.TRNCUSDEC004,:NEW.TRNCUSDEC005,
                :NEW.TRNCUSINT001,:NEW.TRNCUSINT002,:NEW.TRNCUSINT003,:NEW.TRNCUSINT004,:NEW.TRNCUSINT005,
                :NEW.TRNCUSSTR001,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR002,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR003,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR004,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR005,
                :NEW.TRNCUSSTR006,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR007,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR008,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR009,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR010,
                :NEW.TRNCUSSTR011,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR012,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR013,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR014,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR015,
                :NEW.TRNCUSSTR016,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR017,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR018,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR019,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR020,
                :NEW.ACTION,:NEW.REASON_ID,:NEW.TRNSTATUS,:NEW.TRNRCPTOTAL,:NEW.TRNRCPERR,:NEW.TRNRCPSCH,:NEW.TRNRCPPROC,
                :NEW.TRNBCHTOTAL,:NEW.TRNBCHERR,:NEW.TRNBCHSCH,:NEW.TRNBCHPROC,
                :NEW.TRNDATATYPE,:NEW.TRNDATASIZE,:NEW.TRNDATAREF,:NEW.TRNNAPOLTYPE,:NEW.TRNNAPOLSIZE,:NEW.TRNNAPOLREF,
                :NEW.TRNPRTLOGNAME,:NEW.TRNRETHOLD,:NEW.TRNDOLOG,:NEW.SRCTRN_ID);
       ELSIF (:NEW.TRNDOLOG>1) THEN
         Insert into TRNSLOG (JOB_ID,TRN_ID,UNIQUE_ID,KEY1,KEY2,KEY3,KEYID,FORMSETID,
                ARCKEY,RECTYPE,DESCR,TRNNAME,DOCTYPE,DOCSUBTYPE,ORIGUSER,

                FROMUSER,FROMTIME,FROMGROUP,TOTIME,TOUSER,TOGROUP,
                ROUTEDESC,PROCESSNAME,
                TRNAPPDATE001,TRNAPPDATE002,TRNAPPDATE003,TRNAPPDATE004,TRNAPPDATE005,
                TRNAPPDEC001,TRNAPPDEC002,TRNAPPDEC003,TRNAPPDEC004,TRNAPPDEC005,
                TRNAPPINT001,TRNAPPINT002,TRNAPPINT003,TRNAPPINT004,TRNAPPINT005,
                TRNAPPSTR001,TRNAPPSTR002,TRNAPPSTR003,TRNAPPSTR004,TRNAPPSTR005,
                TRNAPPSTR006,TRNAPPSTR007,TRNAPPSTR008,TRNAPPSTR009,TRNAPPSTR010,
                TRNAPPSTR011,TRNAPPSTR012,TRNAPPSTR013,TRNAPPSTR014,TRNAPPSTR015,
                TRNCUSDATE001,TRNCUSDATE002,TRNCUSDATE003,TRNCUSDATE004,TRNCUSDATE005,
                TRNCUSDATE006,TRNCUSDATE007,TRNCUSDATE008,TRNCUSDATE009,TRNCUSDATE010,
                TRNCUSDATE011,TRNCUSDATE012,TRNCUSDATE013,TRNCUSDATE014,TRNCUSDATE015,
                TRNCUSDEC001,TRNCUSDEC002,TRNCUSDEC003,TRNCUSDEC004,TRNCUSDEC005,
                TRNCUSINT001,TRNCUSINT002,TRNCUSINT003,TRNCUSINT004,TRNCUSINT005,
                TRNCUSSTR001,TRNCUSSTR002,TRNCUSSTR003,TRNCUSSTR004,TRNCUSSTR005,
                TRNCUSSTR006,TRNCUSSTR007,TRNCUSSTR008,TRNCUSSTR009,TRNCUSSTR010,
                TRNCUSSTR011,TRNCUSSTR012,TRNCUSSTR013,TRNCUSSTR014,TRNCUSSTR015,
                TRNCUSSTR016,TRNCUSSTR017,TRNCUSSTR018,TRNCUSSTR019,TRNCUSSTR020,
                ACTION,REASON_ID,TRNSTATUS,TRNRCPTOTAL,TRNRCPERR,TRNRCPSCH,TRNRCPPROC,
                TRNBCHTOTAL,TRNBCHERR,TRNBCHSCH,TRNBCHPROC,
                TRNDATATYPE,TRNDATASIZE,TRNDATAREF,TRNNAPOLTYPE,TRNNAPOLSIZE,TRNNAPOLREF,
                TRNNAPOLXML,TRNNAPOLBLOB,
                TRNPRTLOGNAME,TRNRETHOLD,TRNDOLOG,SRCTRN_ID
        ) VALUES (
                :NEW.JOB_ID,:NEW.TRN_ID,:NEW.UNIQUE_ID,:NEW.KEY1,:NEW.KEY2,:NEW.KEY3,:NEW.KEYID,:NEW.FORMSETID,
                :NEW.ARCKEY,:NEW.RECTYPE,:NEW.DESCR,:NEW.TRNNAME,:NEW.DOCTYPE,:NEW.DOCSUBTYPE,:NEW.ORIGUSER,
                :NEW.CURRUSER,:NEW.CURRGROUP,:NEW.CURRROLE,:NEW.CURRSUPER,:NEW.CURRAPP_ID,:NEW.STATUSCODE,:NEW.TRANCODE,
                :NEW.APPROVALSTATE,:NEW.SECLEVEL,:NEW.TRNERR_ID,:NEW.INUSE,:NEW.CUSTOMIZED,:NEW.CREATETIME,
                :NEW.BEGINTIME,:NEW.TRNSTARTTIME,
                TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),
                TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),
                :NEW.ARCTIME,:NEW.RETENTION,:NEW.TRNENDTIME,
                :NEW.ENDTIME,:NEW.JURISDICTN,:NEW.LOCID,:NEW.QUEUEID,:NEW.SUBLOCID,:NEW.AGENCYID,
                :NEW.FROMUSER,:NEW.FROMTIME,:NEW.FROMGROUP,:NEW.TOTIME,:NEW.TOUSER,:NEW.TOGROUP,
                :NEW.ROUTEDESC,:NEW.PROCESSNAME,
                :NEW.TRNAPPDATE001,:NEW.TRNAPPDATE002,:NEW.TRNAPPDATE003,:NEW.TRNAPPDATE004,:NEW.TRNAPPDATE005,
                :NEW.TRNAPPDEC001,:NEW.TRNAPPDEC002,:NEW.TRNAPPDEC003,:NEW.TRNAPPDEC004,:NEW.TRNAPPDEC005,
                :NEW.TRNAPPINT001,:NEW.TRNAPPINT002,:NEW.TRNAPPINT003,:NEW.TRNAPPINT004,:NEW.TRNAPPINT005,
                :NEW.TRNAPPSTR001,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR002,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR003,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR004,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR005,
                :NEW.TRNAPPSTR006,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR007,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR008,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR009,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR010,
                :NEW.TRNAPPSTR011,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR012,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR013,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR014,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR015,
                :NEW.TRNCUSDATE001,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE002,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE003,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE004,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE005,
                :NEW.TRNCUSDATE006,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE007,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE008,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE009,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE010,
                :NEW.TRNCUSDATE011,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE012,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE013,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE014,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE015,
                :NEW.TRNCUSDEC001,:NEW.TRNCUSDEC002,:NEW.TRNCUSDEC003,:NEW.TRNCUSDEC004,:NEW.TRNCUSDEC005,
                :NEW.TRNCUSINT001,:NEW.TRNCUSINT002,:NEW.TRNCUSINT003,:NEW.TRNCUSINT004,:NEW.TRNCUSINT005,
                :NEW.TRNCUSSTR001,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR002,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR003,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR004,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR005,
                :NEW.TRNCUSSTR006,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR007,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR008,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR009,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR010,
                :NEW.TRNCUSSTR011,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR012,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR013,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR014,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR015,
                :NEW.TRNCUSSTR016,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR017,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR018,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR019,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR020,
                :NEW.ACTION,:NEW.REASON_ID,:NEW.TRNSTATUS,:NEW.TRNRCPTOTAL,:NEW.TRNRCPERR,:NEW.TRNRCPSCH,:NEW.TRNRCPPROC,
                :NEW.TRNBCHTOTAL,:NEW.TRNBCHERR,:NEW.TRNBCHSCH,:NEW.TRNBCHPROC,
                :NEW.TRNDATATYPE,:NEW.TRNDATASIZE,:NEW.TRNDATAREF,:NEW.TRNNAPOLTYPE,:NEW.TRNNAPOLSIZE,:NEW.TRNNAPOLREF,
                :NEW.TRNNAPOLXML,:NEW.TRNNAPOLBLOB,
                :NEW.TRNPRTLOGNAME,:NEW.TRNRETHOLD,:NEW.TRNDOLOG,:NEW.SRCTRN_ID);
       END IF;
     END TRNS_AFTERINS_TRG;
/

CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER TRNS_BEFOREUPD_TRG
   BEFORE UPDATE ON TRNS
     FOR EACH ROW
     BEGIN
	IF(:NEW.TRNDOLOG>1) THEN 
           :NEW.TRNAPPINT001:=:NEW.TRNAPPINT001+1; 
        END IF ;
        IF(:NEW.STATUSCODE <> :OLD.STATUSCODE OR (:OLD.STATUSCODE IS NULL AND :NEW.STATUSCODE IS NOT NULL)) THEN
           IF(:NEW.STATUSCODE='B' AND :OLD.STATUSCODE<>'B' AND :NEW.TRNSTATUS>319) THEN 
              :NEW.STATUSCODE:=:OLD.STATUSCODE; 
	   END IF;
           IF(:NEW.STATUSCODE='B' AND :OLD.STATUSCODE='W' AND :NEW.TRNSTATUS<311) THEN 
              :NEW.TRNSTATUS:=311; 
           ELSIF(:NEW.STATUSCODE='W' AND :OLD.STATUSCODE<>'P' AND :NEW.TRNSTATUS<400) THEN 
              :NEW.TRNSTATUS:=290; 
           ELSIF(:NEW.STATUSCODE='D' AND :OLD.STATUSCODE<>'D') THEN 
              :NEW.TRNSTATUS:=288; 
           ELSIF(:NEW.STATUSCODE='E' AND :OLD.STATUSCODE<>'E') THEN 
              :NEW.TRNSTATUS:=241; 
           END IF;
           IF(:NEW.STATUSCODE='W') THEN 
              UPDATE JOBS SET JOBS.JOBTRNWIP=JOBS.JOBTRNWIP+1 WHERE JOBS.JOB_ID=:NEW.JOB_ID;
           END IF;
           IF(:OLD.STATUSCODE='W') THEN 
              UPDATE JOBS SET JOBS.JOBTRNWIP=JOBS.JOBTRNWIP-1 WHERE JOBS.JOB_ID=:NEW.JOB_ID;
           END IF;
           IF(:NEW.STATUSCODE='D') THEN 
              UPDATE JOBS SET JOBS.JOBTRNTOTAL=JOBS.JOBTRNTOTAL-1 WHERE JOBS.JOB_ID=:NEW.JOB_ID;
           END IF;
	   /* Performed by Receiver */
           IF(:OLD.STATUSCODE='D') THEN 
              UPDATE JOBS SET JOBS.JOBTRNTOTAL=JOBS.JOBTRNTOTAL+1 WHERE JOBS.JOB_ID=:NEW.JOB_ID;
           END IF;
        END IF; 
        
        IF (:OLD.TRNRCPSCH<>:NEW.TRNRCPSCH AND
            (:OLD.TRNRCPSCH IS NULL OR :NEW.TRNRCPSCH>:OLD.TRNRCPSCH)) THEN
            UPDATE JOBS SET JOBS.JOBRCPSCH=JOBS.JOBRCPSCH+1 WHERE JOBS.JOB_ID=:NEW.JOB_ID;
        END IF;
        IF (:OLD.TRNRCPTOTAL<1 AND :NEW.TRNRCPTOTAL>0 AND (:NEW.TRNSTATUS<300 OR :NEW.TRNSTATUS IS NULL)) THEN 
           :NEW.TRNSTATUS:=301;
        END IF;
        IF (:NEW.TRNRCPTOTAL<>:OLD.TRNRCPTOTAL AND :NEW.TRNRCPTOTAL>0) THEN
            UPDATE JOBS SET JOBS.JOBRCPTOTAL=JOBS.JOBRCPTOTAL+:NEW.TRNRCPTOTAL WHERE JOBS.JOB_ID=:NEW.JOB_ID;
        END IF;
        IF (:NEW.TRNRCPPROC>:OLD.TRNRCPPROC) THEN
            UPDATE JOBS SET JOBS.JOBRCPPROC=JOBS.JOBRCPPROC+1 WHERE JOBS.JOB_ID=:NEW.JOB_ID;
        END IF;
        IF (:NEW.TRNBCHTOTAL<>:OLD.TRNBCHTOTAL AND :NEW.TRNBCHTOTAL>0) THEN
            UPDATE JOBS SET JOBS.JOBBCHTOTAL=JOBS.JOBBCHTOTAL+:NEW.TRNBCHTOTAL WHERE JOBS.JOB_ID=:NEW.JOB_ID;
        END IF;
        IF (:NEW.TRNBCHPROC>:OLD.TRNBCHPROC) THEN
            UPDATE JOBS SET JOBS.JOBBCHPROC=JOBS.JOBBCHPROC+1 WHERE JOBS.JOB_ID=:NEW.JOB_ID;
        END IF;
        IF (:OLD.TRNBCHSCH<>:NEW.TRNBCHSCH AND
            (:OLD.TRNBCHSCH IS NULL OR :NEW.TRNBCHSCH>:OLD.TRNBCHSCH)) THEN
            UPDATE JOBS SET JOBS.JOBBCHSCH=JOBS.JOBBCHSCH+1 WHERE JOBS.JOB_ID=:NEW.JOB_ID;
        END IF;
        IF (:NEW.TRNBCHERR>:OLD.TRNBCHERR AND :NEW.TRNBCHERR>0 AND (MOD(:NEW.TRNSTATUS,100)<40 OR MOD(:NEW.TRNSTATUS,100)>49)) THEN 
               :NEW.TRNSTATUS:=441;
        END IF;        
        IF (:NEW.TRNBCHTOTAL=:NEW.TRNBCHPROC AND :NEW.TRNBCHTOTAL>0 AND 
            :NEW.TRNRCPTOTAL=:NEW.TRNRCPPROC AND :NEW.TRNRCPTOTAL>0 AND 
            :NEW.TRNSTATUS>=411) THEN 
           SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.TRNENDTIME FROM DUAL;  
           :NEW.TRNSTATUS:=999;
           :NEW.STATUSCODE:='P';
	   IF (:NEW.TRNDOLOG=0) THEN :NEW.TRNDOLOG:=1; END IF;
           :NEW.TRNBCHSCH:=0; 
           :NEW.TRNRCPSCH:=0;
        END IF; 
        IF (:NEW.TRNBCHTOTAL=(:NEW.TRNBCHPROC + :NEW.TRNBCHSCH) AND :NEW.TRNBCHTOTAL>0 AND :NEW.TRNBCHSCH>0 AND
            :NEW.TRNSTATUS>=415) THEN
            :NEW.TRNSTATUS:=416;
        END IF;
        IF (:NEW.TRNBCHERR>:OLD.TRNBCHERR) THEN
            UPDATE JOBS SET JOBS.JOBBCHERR=JOBS.JOBBCHERR+1 WHERE JOBS.JOB_ID=:NEW.JOB_ID;
        END IF;
        IF (:NEW.TRNRCPERR>:OLD.TRNRCPERR) THEN
            UPDATE JOBS SET JOBS.JOBRCPERR=JOBS.JOBRCPERR+1 WHERE JOBS.JOB_ID=:NEW.JOB_ID;
        END IF;
        IF ((:NEW.TRNERR_ID IS NOT NULL AND :NEW.TRNERR_ID>0) AND 
            (:OLD.TRNERR_ID IS NULL OR :OLD.TRNERR_ID<=0) AND 
            (:NEW.TRNSTATUS=:OLD.TRNSTATUS AND :NEW.TRNSTATUS IS NOT NULL) AND 
            (MOD(:NEW.TRNSTATUS,100)<40 OR MOD(:NEW.TRNSTATUS,100)>49)) THEN 
                  :NEW.TRNSTATUS:=(TRUNC(:NEW.TRNSTATUS/100,0))*100+41;
              IF(:NEW.STATUSCODE='W') THEN 
                 UPDATE JOBS SET JOBS.JOBTRNWIP=JOBS.JOBTRNWIP-1 WHERE JOBS.JOB_ID=:NEW.JOB_ID;
              END IF; 
              :NEW.STATUSCODE:='E';
              :NEW.TRNDOLOG:=1;
        ELSIF ((:NEW.TRNERR_ID IS NULL OR :NEW.TRNERR_ID=0) AND (:OLD.TRNERR_ID IS NOT NULL AND :OLD.TRNERR_ID<>0)) THEN 
              UPDATE JOBS SET JOBS.JOBTRNERR=JOBS.JOBTRNERR-1 WHERE JOBS.JOB_ID=:NEW.JOB_ID;
              IF(:NEW.STATUSCODE='W') THEN 
                 UPDATE JOBS SET JOBS.JOBTRNWIP=JOBS.JOBTRNWIP+1 WHERE JOBS.JOB_ID=:NEW.JOB_ID;
              END IF; 
        ELSIF (:NEW.TRNSTATUS<>:OLD.TRNSTATUS AND 
               (MOD(:OLD.TRNSTATUS,100)>=40 AND MOD(:OLD.TRNSTATUS,100)<=49) AND
               (:NEW.TRNSTATUS IS NULL OR MOD(:NEW.TRNSTATUS,100)<40 OR MOD(:NEW.TRNSTATUS,100)>49)) THEN 
              UPDATE JOBS SET JOBS.JOBTRNERR=JOBS.JOBTRNERR-1 WHERE JOBS.JOB_ID=:NEW.JOB_ID;
              IF(:NEW.STATUSCODE='W') THEN 
                 UPDATE JOBS SET JOBS.JOBTRNWIP=JOBS.JOBTRNWIP+1 WHERE JOBS.JOB_ID=:NEW.JOB_ID;
              END IF; 
        ELSIF (:OLD.STATUSCODE='E' AND :NEW.STATUSCODE<>'E') THEN 
              UPDATE JOBS SET JOBS.JOBTRNERR=JOBS.JOBTRNERR-1 WHERE JOBS.JOB_ID=:NEW.JOB_ID;
        END IF;                        

        IF ((:NEW.TRNSTATUS<>:OLD.TRNSTATUS AND :NEW.TRNSTATUS IS NOT NULL AND 
             (MOD(:NEW.TRNSTATUS,100)>=40 AND MOD(:NEW.TRNSTATUS,100)<=49)) AND 
             (:OLD.TRNSTATUS IS NULL OR 
              (:OLD.TRNSTATUS IS NOT NULL AND MOD(:OLD.TRNSTATUS,100)<40 OR MOD(:OLD.TRNSTATUS,100)>49))) THEN 
              :NEW.STATUSCODE:='E';
	      IF (:NEW.TRNDOLOG=0) THEN :NEW.TRNDOLOG:=1; END IF;
              UPDATE JOBS SET JOBS.JOBSTATUS=:NEW.TRNSTATUS,JOBS.JOBTRNERR=JOBS.JOBTRNERR+1 WHERE JOBS.JOB_ID=:NEW.JOB_ID;
              IF(:NEW.STATUSCODE='W') THEN 
                 UPDATE JOBS SET JOBS.JOBTRNWIP=JOBS.JOBTRNWIP-1,JOBS.JOBSTATUS=:NEW.TRNSTATUS WHERE JOBS.JOB_ID=:NEW.JOB_ID;
              END IF; 
        END IF; 
        IF (:NEW.TRNSTATUS=999 AND :OLD.TRNSTATUS<999 ) THEN 
           UPDATE JOBS SET JOBS.JOBTRNPROC=JOBS.JOBTRNPROC+1 WHERE JOBS.JOB_ID=:NEW.JOB_ID;
        END IF; 
        IF (:OLD.TRNSTATUS=999 AND :NEW.TRNSTATUS<999 ) THEN 
           UPDATE JOBS SET JOBS.JOBTRNPROC=JOBS.JOBTRNPROC-1 WHERE JOBS.JOB_ID=:NEW.JOB_ID;
        END IF;
        IF (:NEW.TRNSTATUS=416 AND :OLD.TRNSTATUS<416) THEN
           UPDATE JOBS SET JOBS.JOBTRNSCH=JOBS.JOBTRNSCH+1 WHERE JOBS.JOB_ID=:NEW.JOB_ID;
        END IF;
        IF (:NEW.TRNSTATUS>=311 AND :NEW.TRNSTATUS<=399 ) THEN 
          :NEW.ACTION:=100012;
        ELSIF (:NEW.TRNSTATUS>=411 AND :NEW.TRNSTATUS<=499 ) THEN 
          :NEW.ACTION:=100013;
        ELSIF (:NEW.TRNSTATUS>=511 AND :NEW.TRNSTATUS<=599 ) THEN 
          :NEW.ACTION:=100014;
        ELSIF (:NEW.TRNSTATUS>=611 AND :NEW.TRNSTATUS<=699 ) THEN 
          :NEW.ACTION:=100015;
        ELSIF (:NEW.TRNSTATUS>=711 AND :NEW.TRNSTATUS<=799 ) THEN 
          :NEW.ACTION:=100016;
        ELSIF ( MOD(:NEW.TRNSTATUS,100)=88 ) THEN 
          :NEW.ACTION:=100005;
        ELSIF (:NEW.TRNSTATUS=999 ) THEN 
	      :NEW.ACTION:=100017;
        END IF; 
        SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.TRNMODIFYTIME FROM DUAL;
     END TRNS_BEFOREUPD_TRG;
/


CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER TRNS_AFTERUPD_TRG
   AFTER UPDATE ON TRNS
     FOR EACH ROW WHEN (NEW.TRNDOLOG>0)
     BEGIN
       IF (:NEW.TRNDOLOG=1) THEN
         Insert into TRNSLOG (
                JOB_ID,TRN_ID,UNIQUE_ID,KEY1,KEY2,KEY3,KEYID,FORMSETID,
                ARCKEY,RECTYPE,DESCR,TRNNAME,DOCTYPE,DOCSUBTYPE,ORIGUSER,
                CURRUSER,CURRGROUP,CURRROLE,CURRSUPER,CURRAPP_ID,STATUSCODE,TRANCODE,
                APPROVALSTATE,SECLEVEL,TRNERR_ID,INUSE,CUSTOMIZED,CREATETIME,
                BEGINTIME,TRNSTARTTIME,
                MODIFYTIME,TRNMODIFYTIME,
                ARCTIME,RETENTION,TRNENDTIME,
                ENDTIME,JURISDICTN,LOCID,QUEUEID,SUBLOCID,AGENCYID,
                FROMUSER,FROMTIME,FROMGROUP,TOTIME,TOUSER,TOGROUP,
                ROUTEDESC,PROCESSNAME,
                TRNAPPDATE001,TRNAPPDATE002,TRNAPPDATE003,TRNAPPDATE004,TRNAPPDATE005,
                TRNAPPDEC001,TRNAPPDEC002,TRNAPPDEC003,TRNAPPDEC004,TRNAPPDEC005,
                TRNAPPINT001,TRNAPPINT002,TRNAPPINT003,TRNAPPINT004,TRNAPPINT005,
                TRNAPPSTR001,TRNAPPSTR002,TRNAPPSTR003,TRNAPPSTR004,TRNAPPSTR005,
                TRNAPPSTR006,TRNAPPSTR007,TRNAPPSTR008,TRNAPPSTR009,TRNAPPSTR010,
                TRNAPPSTR011,TRNAPPSTR012,TRNAPPSTR013,TRNAPPSTR014,TRNAPPSTR015,
                TRNCUSDATE001,TRNCUSDATE002,TRNCUSDATE003,TRNCUSDATE004,TRNCUSDATE005,
                TRNCUSDATE006,TRNCUSDATE007,TRNCUSDATE008,TRNCUSDATE009,TRNCUSDATE010,
                TRNCUSDATE011,TRNCUSDATE012,TRNCUSDATE013,TRNCUSDATE014,TRNCUSDATE015,
                TRNCUSDEC001,TRNCUSDEC002,TRNCUSDEC003,TRNCUSDEC004,TRNCUSDEC005,
                TRNCUSINT001,TRNCUSINT002,TRNCUSINT003,TRNCUSINT004,TRNCUSINT005,
                TRNCUSSTR001,TRNCUSSTR002,TRNCUSSTR003,TRNCUSSTR004,TRNCUSSTR005,
                TRNCUSSTR006,TRNCUSSTR007,TRNCUSSTR008,TRNCUSSTR009,TRNCUSSTR010,
                TRNCUSSTR011,TRNCUSSTR012,TRNCUSSTR013,TRNCUSSTR014,TRNCUSSTR015,
                TRNCUSSTR016,TRNCUSSTR017,TRNCUSSTR018,TRNCUSSTR019,TRNCUSSTR020,
                ACTION,REASON_ID,TRNSTATUS,TRNRCPTOTAL,TRNRCPERR,TRNRCPSCH,TRNRCPPROC,
                TRNBCHTOTAL,TRNBCHERR,TRNBCHSCH,TRNBCHPROC,
                TRNDATATYPE,TRNDATASIZE,TRNDATAREF,TRNNAPOLTYPE,TRNNAPOLSIZE,TRNNAPOLREF,
                TRNPRTLOGNAME,TRNRETHOLD,TRNDOLOG,SRCTRN_ID
           ) VALUES (
                :NEW.JOB_ID,:NEW.TRN_ID,:NEW.UNIQUE_ID,:NEW.KEY1,:NEW.KEY2,:NEW.KEY3,:NEW.KEYID,:NEW.FORMSETID,
                :NEW.ARCKEY,:NEW.RECTYPE,:NEW.DESCR,:NEW.TRNNAME,:NEW.DOCTYPE,:NEW.DOCSUBTYPE,:NEW.ORIGUSER,
                :NEW.CURRUSER,:NEW.CURRGROUP,:NEW.CURRROLE,:NEW.CURRSUPER,:NEW.CURRAPP_ID,:NEW.STATUSCODE,:NEW.TRANCODE,
                :NEW.APPROVALSTATE,:NEW.SECLEVEL,:NEW.TRNERR_ID,:NEW.INUSE,:NEW.CUSTOMIZED,:NEW.CREATETIME,
                :NEW.BEGINTIME,:NEW.TRNSTARTTIME,
                TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),
                TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),
                :NEW.ARCTIME,:NEW.RETENTION,:NEW.TRNENDTIME,
                :NEW.ENDTIME,:NEW.JURISDICTN,:NEW.LOCID,:NEW.QUEUEID,:NEW.SUBLOCID,:NEW.AGENCYID,
                :NEW.FROMUSER,:NEW.FROMTIME,:NEW.FROMGROUP,:NEW.TOTIME,:NEW.TOUSER,:NEW.TOGROUP,
                :NEW.ROUTEDESC,:NEW.PROCESSNAME,
                :NEW.TRNAPPDATE001,:NEW.TRNAPPDATE002,:NEW.TRNAPPDATE003,:NEW.TRNAPPDATE004,:NEW.TRNAPPDATE005,
                :NEW.TRNAPPDEC001,:NEW.TRNAPPDEC002,:NEW.TRNAPPDEC003,:NEW.TRNAPPDEC004,:NEW.TRNAPPDEC005,
                :NEW.TRNAPPINT001,:NEW.TRNAPPINT002,:NEW.TRNAPPINT003,:NEW.TRNAPPINT004,:NEW.TRNAPPINT005,
                :NEW.TRNAPPSTR001,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR002,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR003,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR004,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR005,
                :NEW.TRNAPPSTR006,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR007,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR008,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR009,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR010,
                :NEW.TRNAPPSTR011,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR012,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR013,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR014,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR015,
                :NEW.TRNCUSDATE001,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE002,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE003,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE004,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE005,
                :NEW.TRNCUSDATE006,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE007,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE008,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE009,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE010,
                :NEW.TRNCUSDATE011,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE012,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE013,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE014,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE015,
                :NEW.TRNCUSDEC001,:NEW.TRNCUSDEC002,:NEW.TRNCUSDEC003,:NEW.TRNCUSDEC004,:NEW.TRNCUSDEC005,
                :NEW.TRNCUSINT001,:NEW.TRNCUSINT002,:NEW.TRNCUSINT003,:NEW.TRNCUSINT004,:NEW.TRNCUSINT005,
                :NEW.TRNCUSSTR001,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR002,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR003,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR004,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR005,
                :NEW.TRNCUSSTR006,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR007,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR008,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR009,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR010,
                :NEW.TRNCUSSTR011,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR012,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR013,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR014,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR015,
                :NEW.TRNCUSSTR016,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR017,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR018,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR019,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR020,
                :NEW.ACTION,:NEW.REASON_ID,:NEW.TRNSTATUS,:NEW.TRNRCPTOTAL,:NEW.TRNRCPERR,:NEW.TRNRCPSCH,:NEW.TRNRCPPROC,
                :NEW.TRNBCHTOTAL,:NEW.TRNBCHERR,:NEW.TRNBCHSCH,:NEW.TRNBCHPROC,
                :NEW.TRNDATATYPE,:NEW.TRNDATASIZE,:NEW.TRNDATAREF,:NEW.TRNNAPOLTYPE,:NEW.TRNNAPOLSIZE,:NEW.TRNNAPOLREF,
                :NEW.TRNPRTLOGNAME,:NEW.TRNRETHOLD,:NEW.TRNDOLOG,:NEW.SRCTRN_ID);
        ELSIF (:NEW.TRNDOLOG>1) THEN
            Insert into TRNSLOG (
                JOB_ID,TRN_ID,UNIQUE_ID,KEY1,KEY2,KEY3,KEYID,FORMSETID,

                ENDTIME,JURISDICTN,LOCID,QUEUEID,SUBLOCID,AGENCYID,
                FROMUSER,FROMTIME,FROMGROUP,TOTIME,TOUSER,TOGROUP,
                ROUTEDESC,PROCESSNAME,
                TRNAPPDATE001,TRNAPPDATE002,TRNAPPDATE003,TRNAPPDATE004,TRNAPPDATE005,
                TRNAPPDEC001,TRNAPPDEC002,TRNAPPDEC003,TRNAPPDEC004,TRNAPPDEC005,
                TRNAPPINT001,TRNAPPINT002,TRNAPPINT003,TRNAPPINT004,TRNAPPINT005,
                TRNAPPSTR001,TRNAPPSTR002,TRNAPPSTR003,TRNAPPSTR004,TRNAPPSTR005,
                TRNAPPSTR006,TRNAPPSTR007,TRNAPPSTR008,TRNAPPSTR009,TRNAPPSTR010,
                TRNAPPSTR011,TRNAPPSTR012,TRNAPPSTR013,TRNAPPSTR014,TRNAPPSTR015,
                TRNCUSDATE001,TRNCUSDATE002,TRNCUSDATE003,TRNCUSDATE004,TRNCUSDATE005,
                TRNCUSDATE006,TRNCUSDATE007,TRNCUSDATE008,TRNCUSDATE009,TRNCUSDATE010,
                TRNCUSDATE011,TRNCUSDATE012,TRNCUSDATE013,TRNCUSDATE014,TRNCUSDATE015,
                TRNCUSDEC001,TRNCUSDEC002,TRNCUSDEC003,TRNCUSDEC004,TRNCUSDEC005,
                TRNCUSINT001,TRNCUSINT002,TRNCUSINT003,TRNCUSINT004,TRNCUSINT005,
                TRNCUSSTR001,TRNCUSSTR002,TRNCUSSTR003,TRNCUSSTR004,TRNCUSSTR005,
                TRNCUSSTR006,TRNCUSSTR007,TRNCUSSTR008,TRNCUSSTR009,TRNCUSSTR010,
                TRNCUSSTR011,TRNCUSSTR012,TRNCUSSTR013,TRNCUSSTR014,TRNCUSSTR015,
                TRNCUSSTR016,TRNCUSSTR017,TRNCUSSTR018,TRNCUSSTR019,TRNCUSSTR020,
                ACTION,REASON_ID,TRNSTATUS,TRNRCPTOTAL,TRNRCPERR,TRNRCPSCH,TRNRCPPROC,
                TRNBCHTOTAL,TRNBCHERR,TRNBCHSCH,TRNBCHPROC,
                TRNDATATYPE,TRNDATASIZE,TRNDATAREF,TRNNAPOLTYPE,TRNNAPOLSIZE,TRNNAPOLREF,
                TRNNAPOLXML,TRNNAPOLBLOB,
                TRNPRTLOGNAME,TRNRETHOLD,TRNDOLOG,SRCTRN_ID
           ) VALUES (
                :NEW.JOB_ID,:NEW.TRN_ID,:NEW.UNIQUE_ID,:NEW.KEY1,:NEW.KEY2,:NEW.KEY3,:NEW.KEYID,:NEW.FORMSETID,
                :NEW.ARCKEY,:NEW.RECTYPE,:NEW.DESCR,:NEW.TRNNAME,:NEW.DOCTYPE,:NEW.DOCSUBTYPE,:NEW.ORIGUSER,
                :NEW.CURRUSER,:NEW.CURRGROUP,:NEW.CURRROLE,:NEW.CURRSUPER,:NEW.CURRAPP_ID,:NEW.STATUSCODE,:NEW.TRANCODE,
                :NEW.APPROVALSTATE,:NEW.SECLEVEL,:NEW.TRNERR_ID,:NEW.INUSE,:NEW.CUSTOMIZED,:NEW.CREATETIME,
                :NEW.BEGINTIME,:NEW.TRNSTARTTIME,
                TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),
                TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),
                :NEW.ARCTIME,:NEW.RETENTION,:NEW.TRNENDTIME,
                :NEW.ENDTIME,:NEW.JURISDICTN,:NEW.LOCID,:NEW.QUEUEID,:NEW.SUBLOCID,:NEW.AGENCYID,
                :NEW.FROMUSER,:NEW.FROMTIME,:NEW.FROMGROUP,:NEW.TOTIME,:NEW.TOUSER,:NEW.TOGROUP,
                :NEW.ROUTEDESC,:NEW.PROCESSNAME,
                :NEW.TRNAPPDATE001,:NEW.TRNAPPDATE002,:NEW.TRNAPPDATE003,:NEW.TRNAPPDATE004,:NEW.TRNAPPDATE005,
                :NEW.TRNAPPDEC001,:NEW.TRNAPPDEC002,:NEW.TRNAPPDEC003,:NEW.TRNAPPDEC004,:NEW.TRNAPPDEC005,
                :NEW.TRNAPPINT001,:NEW.TRNAPPINT002,:NEW.TRNAPPINT003,:NEW.TRNAPPINT004,:NEW.TRNAPPINT005,
                :NEW.TRNAPPSTR001,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR002,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR003,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR004,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR005,
                :NEW.TRNAPPSTR006,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR007,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR008,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR009,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR010,
                :NEW.TRNAPPSTR011,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR012,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR013,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR014,:NEW.TRNAPPSTR015,
                :NEW.TRNCUSDATE001,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE002,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE003,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE004,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE005,
                :NEW.TRNCUSDATE006,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE007,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE008,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE009,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE010,
                :NEW.TRNCUSDATE011,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE012,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE013,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE014,:NEW.TRNCUSDATE015,
                :NEW.TRNCUSDEC001,:NEW.TRNCUSDEC002,:NEW.TRNCUSDEC003,:NEW.TRNCUSDEC004,:NEW.TRNCUSDEC005,
                :NEW.TRNCUSINT001,:NEW.TRNCUSINT002,:NEW.TRNCUSINT003,:NEW.TRNCUSINT004,:NEW.TRNCUSINT005,
                :NEW.TRNCUSSTR001,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR002,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR003,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR004,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR005,
                :NEW.TRNCUSSTR006,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR007,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR008,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR009,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR010,
                :NEW.TRNCUSSTR011,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR012,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR013,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR014,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR015,
                :NEW.TRNCUSSTR016,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR017,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR018,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR019,:NEW.TRNCUSSTR020,
                :NEW.ACTION,:NEW.REASON_ID,:NEW.TRNSTATUS,:NEW.TRNRCPTOTAL,:NEW.TRNRCPERR,:NEW.TRNRCPSCH,:NEW.TRNRCPPROC,
                :NEW.TRNBCHTOTAL,:NEW.TRNBCHERR,:NEW.TRNBCHSCH,:NEW.TRNBCHPROC,
                :NEW.TRNDATATYPE,:NEW.TRNDATASIZE,:NEW.TRNDATAREF,:NEW.TRNNAPOLTYPE,:NEW.TRNNAPOLSIZE,:NEW.TRNNAPOLREF,
                :NEW.TRNNAPOLXML,:NEW.TRNNAPOLBLOB,
                :NEW.TRNPRTLOGNAME,:NEW.TRNRETHOLD,:NEW.TRNDOLOG,:NEW.SRCTRN_ID);
        END IF;
     END TRNS_AFTERUPD_TRG;
/

CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER TRNSHIST_INS_TRG
   BEFORE DELETE ON TRNS
      FOR EACH ROW 
      BEGIN
         IF(:OLD.TRNHISTORY=0) THEN
            UPDATE JOBS SET JOBS.JOBTRNTOTAL=JOBS.JOBTRNTOTAL-1 WHERE JOBS.JOB_ID=:OLD.JOB_ID;
         ELSE
            Insert into TRNSHIST (
                JOB_ID,TRN_ID,UNIQUE_ID,KEY1,KEY2,KEY3,KEYID,FORMSETID,
                ARCKEY,RECTYPE,DESCR,TRNNAME,DOCTYPE,DOCSUBTYPE,ORIGUSER,
                CURRUSER,CURRGROUP,CURRROLE,CURRSUPER,CURRAPP_ID,STATUSCODE,TRANCODE,
                APPROVALSTATE,SECLEVEL,TRNERR_ID,INUSE,CUSTOMIZED,CREATETIME,
                BEGINTIME,TRNSTARTTIME,MODIFYTIME,TRNMODIFYTIME,ARCTIME,RETENTION,TRNENDTIME,
                ENDTIME,JURISDICTN,LOCID,QUEUEID,SUBLOCID,AGENCYID,
                FROMUSER,FROMTIME,FROMGROUP,TOTIME,TOUSER,TOGROUP,
                ROUTEDESC,PROCESSNAME,
                TRNAPPDATE001,TRNAPPDATE002,TRNAPPDATE003,TRNAPPDATE004,TRNAPPDATE005,
                TRNAPPDEC001,TRNAPPDEC002,TRNAPPDEC003,TRNAPPDEC004,TRNAPPDEC005,
                TRNAPPINT001,TRNAPPINT002,TRNAPPINT003,TRNAPPINT004,TRNAPPINT005,
                TRNAPPSTR001,TRNAPPSTR002,TRNAPPSTR003,TRNAPPSTR004,TRNAPPSTR005,
                TRNAPPSTR006,TRNAPPSTR007,TRNAPPSTR008,TRNAPPSTR009,TRNAPPSTR010,
                TRNAPPSTR011,TRNAPPSTR012,TRNAPPSTR013,TRNAPPSTR014,TRNAPPSTR015,
                TRNCUSDATE001,TRNCUSDATE002,TRNCUSDATE003,TRNCUSDATE004,TRNCUSDATE005,
                TRNCUSDATE006,TRNCUSDATE007,TRNCUSDATE008,TRNCUSDATE009,TRNCUSDATE010,
                TRNCUSDATE011,TRNCUSDATE012,TRNCUSDATE013,TRNCUSDATE014,TRNCUSDATE015,
                TRNCUSDEC001,TRNCUSDEC002,TRNCUSDEC003,TRNCUSDEC004,TRNCUSDEC005,
                TRNCUSINT001,TRNCUSINT002,TRNCUSINT003,TRNCUSINT004,TRNCUSINT005,
                TRNCUSSTR001,TRNCUSSTR002,TRNCUSSTR003,TRNCUSSTR004,TRNCUSSTR005,
                TRNCUSSTR006,TRNCUSSTR007,TRNCUSSTR008,TRNCUSSTR009,TRNCUSSTR010,
                TRNCUSSTR011,TRNCUSSTR012,TRNCUSSTR013,TRNCUSSTR014,TRNCUSSTR015,
                TRNCUSSTR016,TRNCUSSTR017,TRNCUSSTR018,TRNCUSSTR019,TRNCUSSTR020,
                ACTION,REASON_ID,TRNSTATUS,TRNRCPTOTAL,TRNRCPERR,TRNRCPSCH,TRNRCPPROC,
                TRNBCHTOTAL,TRNBCHERR,TRNBCHSCH,TRNBCHPROC,TRNDATATYPE,TRNDATAREF,TRNDATAXML,TRNDATABLOB,TRNDATASIZE,
                TRNNAPOLTYPE,TRNNAPOLREF,TRNNAPOLXML,TRNNAPOLBLOB,TRNNAPOLSIZE,TRNPRTLOGNAME,TRNDOLOG,TRNRETHOLD,TRNHISTORY,SRCTRN_ID
            ) VALUES (
                :OLD.JOB_ID,:OLD.TRN_ID,:OLD.UNIQUE_ID,:OLD.KEY1,:OLD.KEY2,:OLD.KEY3,:OLD.KEYID,:OLD.FORMSETID,
                :OLD.ARCKEY,:OLD.RECTYPE,:OLD.DESCR,:OLD.TRNNAME,:OLD.DOCTYPE,:OLD.DOCSUBTYPE,:OLD.ORIGUSER,

CREATE SEQUENCE STRCODE_SEQ MINVALUE 1 MAXVALUE 999999999999999999999999999 INCREMENT BY 1 START WITH 1 CYCLE;
CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER ASSIGN_STRCODE_SEQ 
   BEFORE INSERT ON TRANSTATUSCODES
      FOR EACH ROW
         BEGIN
            IF :NEW.STRCODEID IS NULL OR :NEW.STRCODEID < 0 THEN
               SELECT STRCODE_SEQ.NEXTVAL INTO :NEW.STRCODEID FROM DUAL;
            END IF;
         END ASSIGN_STRCODE_SEQ;
/

CREATE SEQUENCE PUBS_PUB_ID_SEQ MINVALUE 1 MAXVALUE 999999999999999999999999999 INCREMENT BY 1 START WITH 1 CYCLE;
CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER PUBS_PUB_ID_TRG 
   BEFORE INSERT ON PUBS 
      FOR EACH ROW 
         BEGIN 
            IF (:NEW.PUB_ID is null OR :NEW.PUB_ID = 0) THEN
               SELECT PUBS_PUB_ID_SEQ.nextval INTO :NEW.PUB_ID FROM DUAL; 
            END IF;
            SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.PUBSTARTTIME FROM DUAL;
            IF(:NEW.PUBSTATUS=999) THEN 
              SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.PUBENDTIME FROM DUAL;
            END IF;
         END PUBS_PUB_ID_TRG;
/

CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER PUBS_PUBENDTIME_TRG 
   BEFORE UPDATE ON PUBS 
      FOR EACH ROW 
         BEGIN 
            SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.PUBENDTIME FROM DUAL;
         END PUBS_PUBENDTIME_TRG;
/

CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER BCHS_RCPS_INS_TRG 
   BEFORE INSERT ON BCHS_RCPS
      FOR EACH ROW 
         BEGIN 
            SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.BCHRCPCREATETIME FROM DUAL;
         END BCHS_RCPS_INS_ID_TRG;
/

      FOR EACH ROW WHEN (OLD.PUBHISTORY = 1) 
      BEGIN

                PUBARCHIVED,PUBARCDOCTYPE,PUBARCDOCSUBTYPE,PUBARCDOCNAME,PUBARCREF,PUBARCTITLE,PUBARCSTATUS,PUBARCSTARTTIME,PUBARCENDTIME,
                PUBSIGNED,PUBSGNDOCTYPE,PUBSGNDOCSUBTYPE,PUBSGNDOCNAME,PUBSGNREF,PUBSGNTITLE,PUBSGNSTATUS,PUBSGNSTARTTIME,PUBSGNENDTIME,
                PUBPUBLISHED,PUBMIMETYPE,PUBPRTLOGNAME,PUBPRTPHYNAME,PUBPUBSTATUS,PUBPUBSTARTTIME,PUBPUBENDTIME,
                PUBNOTIFIED,PUBNTFTYPE,PUBNTFMSGTYP,PUBNTFSTATUS,PUBNTFSTARTTIME,PUBNTFENDTIME,
                PUBAPPDATE001,PUBAPPDATE002,PUBAPPDATE003,PUBAPPDATE004,PUBAPPDATE005,
                PUBAPPDEC001,PUBAPPDEC002,PUBAPPDEC003,PUBAPPDEC004,PUBAPPDEC005,

                PUBAPPSTR011,PUBAPPSTR012,PUBAPPSTR013,PUBAPPSTR014,PUBAPPSTR015,
                PUBCUSDATE001,PUBCUSDATE002,PUBCUSDATE003,PUBCUSDATE004,PUBCUSDATE005,

                PUBCUSINT001,PUBCUSINT002,PUBCUSINT003,PUBCUSINT004,PUBCUSINT005, 
                PUBCUSSTR001,PUBCUSSTR002,PUBCUSSTR003,PUBCUSSTR004,PUBCUSSTR005, 
                PUBCUSSTR006,PUBCUSSTR007,PUBCUSSTR008,PUBCUSSTR009,PUBCUSSTR010,

                :OLD.PUBSEQ,:OLD.PUBPRTTYPE,:OLD.PUBPRTEXT,:OLD.PUBSTATUS,:OLD.PUBSIGNOFF,:OLD.PUBSIGNOFFTIME,

CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER BCHS_RCPSHIST_INS_TRG
   BEFORE DELETE ON BCHS_RCPS
      FOR EACH ROW 
      BEGIN
         IF(:OLD.BCHRCPHISTORY=0) THEN
            UPDATE RCPS SET RCPS.RCPBCHTOTAL=RCPS.RCPBCHTOTAL-1 WHERE RCPS.RCP_ID=:OLD.RCP_ID;
         ELSE
            Insert into BCHS_RCPSHIST (
                BCH_ID,RCP_ID,TRN_ID,JOB_ID,PUB_ID,RCPSEQ,
                BCHRCPACTIVE,BCHRCPBNDLLOC,BCHRCPCREATETIME,BCHRCPERRTIME,BCHRCPSTATUS,BCHRCPPROCTIME,
                BCHRCPCUSDATE001,BCHRCPCUSINT001,BCHRCPCUSDEC001,BCHRCPCUSSTR001,BCHRCPCUSSTR002,BCHRCPGRPSEQ,BCHRCPGRPTOT,BCHRCPHISTORY,BCHRCPTYPE
            ) VALUES (
                :OLD.BCH_ID,:OLD.RCP_ID,:OLD.TRN_ID,:OLD.JOB_ID,:OLD.PUB_ID,:OLD.RCPSEQ,
                :OLD.BCHRCPACTIVE,:OLD.BCHRCPBNDLLOC,:OLD.BCHRCPCREATETIME,:OLD.BCHRCPERRTIME,:OLD.BCHRCPSTATUS,:OLD.BCHRCPPROCTIME,
                :OLD.BCHRCPCUSDATE001,:OLD.BCHRCPCUSINT001,:OLD.BCHRCPCUSDEC001,:OLD.BCHRCPCUSSTR001,:OLD.BCHRCPCUSSTR002,:OLD.BCHRCPGRPSEQ,:OLD.BCHRCPGRPTOT,:OLD.BCHRCPHISTORY,:OLD.BCHRCPTYPE
            ) ;
         END IF;
      END BCHS_RCPSHIST_INS_TRG;
/


CREATE SEQUENCE BCHINGS_BCHING_ID_SEQ MINVALUE 1 MAXVALUE 999999999999999999999999999 INCREMENT BY 1 START WITH 1 CYCLE;
CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER BCHINGS_BCHING_ID_TRG 
   BEFORE INSERT ON BCHINGS
      FOR EACH ROW 
         BEGIN 
            IF (:NEW.BCHING_ID is null OR :NEW.BCHING_ID = 0) THEN
               SELECT BCHINGS_BCHING_ID_SEQ.nextval INTO :NEW.BCHING_ID FROM DUAL; 
            END IF;
         END BCHINGS_BCHING_ID_TRG;
/

CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER LOCKS_INS_TRG 
   BEFORE INSERT ON LOCKS
      FOR EACH ROW 
         BEGIN 
            SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.LASTUPDATETIME FROM DUAL;
         END LOCKS_INS_TRG;
/


CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER LOCKS_UPD_TRG 
   BEFORE UPDATE ON LOCKS
      FOR EACH ROW 
         BEGIN 
            SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.LASTUPDATETIME FROM DUAL;
         END LOCKS_UPD_TRG;
/


CREATE SEQUENCE PRTLOGICS_PRTLOG_ID_SEQ MINVALUE 1 MAXVALUE 999999999999999999999999999 INCREMENT BY 1 START WITH 1 CYCLE;
CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER PRTLOGICS_PRTLOG_ID_TRG 
   BEFORE INSERT ON PRTLOGICS 
      FOR EACH ROW 
         BEGIN 
            IF (:NEW.PRTLOG_ID is null OR :NEW.PRTLOG_ID = 0) THEN
               SELECT PRTLOGICS_PRTLOG_ID_SEQ.nextval INTO :NEW.PRTLOG_ID FROM DUAL; 
            END IF;
            SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.PRTLOGSTATUSTIME FROM DUAL;
         END PRTLOGICS_PRTLOG_ID_TRG;
/

CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER PRTLOGICS_UPD_TRG 
   BEFORE UPDATE ON PRTLOGICS
      FOR EACH ROW 
         BEGIN 
            SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.PRTLOGSTATUSTIME FROM DUAL;
         END PRTLOGICS_UPD_TRG;
/

CREATE SEQUENCE PRTPHYS_PRTPHY_ID_SEQ MINVALUE 1 MAXVALUE 999999999999999999999999999 INCREMENT BY 1 START WITH 1 CYCLE;
CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER PRTPHYS_PRTPHY_ID_TRG 
   BEFORE INSERT ON PRTPHYS
      FOR EACH ROW 
         BEGIN 
            IF (:NEW.PRTPHY_ID is null OR :NEW.PRTPHY_ID = 0) THEN
               SELECT PRTPHYS_PRTPHY_ID_SEQ.nextval INTO :NEW.PRTPHY_ID FROM DUAL; 
            END IF;
            SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.PRTPHYSTATUSTIME FROM DUAL;
         END PRTPHYS_PRTPHY_ID_TRG;
/

CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER PRTPHYS_UPD_TRG 
   BEFORE UPDATE ON PRTPHYS
      FOR EACH ROW 
         BEGIN 
            SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.PRTPHYSTATUSTIME FROM DUAL;
         END PRTPHYS_UPD_TRG;
/

CREATE SEQUENCE PRTPHYCFGS_PRTPHYCFG_ID_SEQ MINVALUE 1 MAXVALUE 999999999999999999999999999 INCREMENT BY 1 START WITH 1 CYCLE;
CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER PRTPHYCFGS_PRTPHYCFG_ID_TRG 
   BEFORE INSERT ON PRTPHYCFGS
      FOR EACH ROW 
         BEGIN 
            IF (:NEW.PRTPHYCFG_ID is null OR :NEW.PRTPHYCFG_ID = 0) THEN
               SELECT PRTPHYCFGS_PRTPHYCFG_ID_SEQ.nextval INTO :NEW.PRTPHYCFG_ID FROM DUAL; 
            END IF;
         END PRTPHYCFGS_PRTLOGCFG_ID_TRG;
/

CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER BCHS_RCPS_BEFOREINS_TRG
   BEFORE INSERT ON BCHS_RCPS
      FOR EACH ROW
         BEGIN
            IF (:NEW.BCHRCPTYPE > 0) THEN
               UPDATE RCPS SET RCPS.RCPBCHSCH=RCPS.RCPBCHSCH+1 WHERE RCPS.RCP_ID=:NEW.RCP_ID;
            END IF;
         END BCHS_RCPS_BEFOREINS_TRG;
/

CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER BCHS_RCPS_BEFOREUPD_TRG 
   BEFORE UPDATE ON BCHS_RCPS
      FOR EACH ROW 
         BEGIN
           IF (:NEW.BCHRCPSTATUS<>:OLD.BCHRCPSTATUS AND :NEW.BCHRCPSTATUS>415) THEN 
               UPDATE RCPS SET RCPS.RCPSTATUS=:NEW.BCHRCPSTATUS WHERE RCPS.RCP_ID=:NEW.RCP_ID;
           END IF;
           IF (:NEW.BCHRCPPROCTIME IS NOT NULL AND :OLD.BCHRCPPROCTIME IS NULL) THEN 
               UPDATE RCPS SET RCPS.RCPBCHPROC=RCPS.RCPBCHPROC+1 WHERE RCPS.RCP_ID=:NEW.RCP_ID;
           ELSIF (:NEW.BCHRCPERRTIME IS NOT NULL AND :OLD.BCHRCPERRTIME IS NULL) THEN 
               UPDATE RCPS SET RCPS.RCPBCHERR=RCPS.RCPBCHERR+1 WHERE RCPS.RCP_ID=:NEW.RCP_ID;
           ELSIF (:NEW.BCHRCPPROCTIME IS NULL AND :OLD.BCHRCPPROCTIME IS NOT NULL) THEN 
               UPDATE RCPS SET RCPS.RCPBCHPROC=RCPS.RCPBCHPROC-1 WHERE RCPS.RCP_ID=:NEW.RCP_ID;
           ELSIF (:NEW.BCHRCPERRTIME IS NULL AND :OLD.BCHRCPERRTIME IS NOT NULL) THEN 
               UPDATE RCPS SET RCPS.RCPBCHERR=RCPS.RCPBCHERR-1 WHERE RCPS.RCP_ID=:NEW.RCP_ID;
           END IF;
         END BCHS_RCPS_BEFOREUPD_TRG;
/


CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER RCPS_BEFOREUPD_TRG 
   BEFORE UPDATE ON RCPS 
      FOR EACH ROW 
      BEGIN
        IF (:NEW.RCPBCHPROC>:OLD.RCPBCHPROC) THEN
            UPDATE TRNS SET TRNS.TRNBCHPROC=TRNS.TRNBCHPROC+1 WHERE TRNS.TRN_ID=:NEW.TRN_ID;
        END IF;
        /* Increment the Transaction scheduled batch count by 1. */
        IF (:NEW.RCPBCHSCH>:OLD.RCPBCHSCH) THEN
            UPDATE TRNS SET TRNS.TRNBCHSCH=TRNS.TRNBCHSCH+1 WHERE TRNS.TRN_ID=:NEW.TRN_ID;
        END IF;
        IF (:NEW.RCPBCHERR>:OLD.RCPBCHERR AND :NEW.RCPBCHERR>0 AND 
            ((MOD(:NEW.RCPSTATUS,100)<40 OR MOD(:NEW.RCPSTATUS,100)>49) AND 
             (:OLD.RCPSTATUS IS NULL OR (MOD(:OLD.RCPSTATUS,100)<40 OR MOD(:OLD.RCPSTATUS,100)>49)))) THEN 
               :NEW.RCPSTATUS:=441;
        END IF;
        IF ((:NEW.RCPSTATUS<>:OLD.RCPSTATUS AND :NEW.RCPSTATUS IS NOT NULL AND MOD(:NEW.RCPSTATUS,100)>=40 AND MOD(:NEW.RCPSTATUS,100)<=49)) THEN 
              UPDATE TRNS SET TRNS.TRNSTATUS=:NEW.RCPSTATUS,TRNS.TRNRCPERR=TRNS.TRNRCPERR+1,TRNS.TRNDOLOG=1 WHERE TRNS.TRN_ID=:NEW.TRN_ID;
        ELSIF ((:NEW.RCPSTATUS<>:OLD.RCPSTATUS AND :NEW.RCPSTATUS IS NOT NULL AND 
               (MOD(:NEW.RCPSTATUS,100)<40 OR MOD(:NEW.RCPSTATUS,100)>49) AND 
               (MOD(:OLD.RCPSTATUS,100)>=40 AND MOD(:OLD.RCPSTATUS,100)<=49))) THEN 
              UPDATE TRNS SET TRNS.TRNRCPERR=TRNS.TRNRCPERR-1,TRNS.TRNDOLOG=0 WHERE TRNS.TRN_ID=:NEW.TRN_ID;
        ELSIF ((:NEW.RCPERR_ID IS NULL OR :NEW.RCPERR_ID=0) AND 
               (:OLD.RCPERR_ID IS NOT NULL AND :OLD.RCPERR_ID>0)) THEN 
              UPDATE TRNS SET TRNS.TRNRCPERR=TRNS.TRNRCPERR-1,TRNS.TRNDOLOG=0 WHERE TRNS.TRN_ID=:NEW.TRN_ID;
        ELSIF ((:NEW.RCPERR_ID IS NOT NULL AND :NEW.RCPERR_ID>0) AND (:OLD.RCPERR_ID IS NULL OR :OLD.RCPERR_ID<=0)) THEN 
              UPDATE TRNS SET TRNS.TRNRCPERR=TRNS.TRNRCPERR+1,TRNS.TRNDOLOG=0 WHERE TRNS.TRN_ID=:NEW.TRN_ID;
        END IF;   
        IF ((:NEW.RCPBCHERR IS NOT NULL AND :NEW.RCPBCHERR>0) AND (:OLD.RCPBCHERR IS NULL OR :OLD.RCPBCHERR<=0)) AND (:OLD.RCPBCHERR<>:NEW.RCPBCHERR) THEN 
              UPDATE TRNS SET TRNS.TRNBCHERR=TRNS.TRNBCHERR+(:NEW.RCPBCHERR-:OLD.RCPBCHERR),TRNS.TRNDOLOG=0 WHERE TRNS.TRN_ID=:NEW.TRN_ID;
        END IF;   
        IF (:NEW.RCPSTATUS=999 AND :NEW.RCPBCHTOTAL<>:NEW.RCPBCHPROC AND :NEW.RCPBCHTOTAL>0) THEN 
           :NEW.RCPSTATUS:=:OLD.RCPSTATUS;
        ELSIF (:NEW.RCPBCHTOTAL>0 AND
               :NEW.RCPBCHTOTAL=:NEW.RCPBCHPROC) THEN 
           SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.RCPENDTIME FROM DUAL;             
           :NEW.RCPSTATUS:=999;
           :NEW.RCPBCHSCH:=0;
        END IF;
        /* Do this only once */
        IF (:NEW.RCPSTATUS=415 AND
            :OLD.RCPSTATUS<>415 AND
            :OLD.RCPBCHSCH>0 AND
            :OLD.RCPBCHERR=0) THEN
           /* Update the recipient scheduled count by 1. */
           UPDATE TRNS SET TRNS.TRNRCPSCH=TRNS.TRNRCPSCH+1 WHERE TRNS.TRN_ID=:NEW.TRN_ID;
        END IF;   
        /* Do this only once */
        IF (:NEW.RCPSTATUS=999 AND
            :OLD.RCPSTATUS<>999) THEN
           /* Update the recipient processed count by 1. */
           UPDATE TRNS SET TRNS.TRNRCPPROC=TRNS.TRNRCPPROC+1,TRNS.TRNDOLOG=0 WHERE TRNS.TRN_ID=:NEW.TRN_ID;
        END IF;  
      END RCPS_BEFOREUPD_TRG;
/

CREATE SEQUENCE TAGS_TAG_ID_SEQ MINVALUE 1 MAXVALUE 999999999999999999999999999 INCREMENT BY 1 START WITH 1 CYCLE;
CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER TAGS_TAG_ID_TRG 
   BEFORE INSERT ON TAGS
      FOR EACH ROW 
         BEGIN 
            IF (:NEW.TAG_ID is null OR :NEW.TAG_ID = 0) THEN
               SELECT TAGS_TAG_ID_SEQ.nextval INTO :NEW.TAG_ID FROM DUAL; 
            END IF;
            SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.TAGCREATETIME FROM DUAL;
         END TAGS_TAG_ID_TRG;
/

COMMIT;

    ( 
     aid NUMBER(38)  NOT NULL , 
     tid NVARCHAR2 (80)  NOT NULL , 
     firstname NVARCHAR2 (100) , 
     lastname NVARCHAR2 (100) , 
     type NVARCHAR2 (20) , 
     role NVARCHAR2 (100) , 
     address1 NVARCHAR2 (100) , 
     address2 NVARCHAR2 (100) , 
     attachments NUMBER DEFAULT 1 , 
     CITY NVARCHAR2 (100) , 
     COUNTRY NVARCHAR2 (20) , 
     EMAIL NVARCHAR2 (100) , 
     FAX NVARCHAR2 (20) , 
     PHONE NVARCHAR2 (20) , 
     POSTALCODE NVARCHAR2 (20) , 
     PREFERREDDIST NVARCHAR2 (100) , 
     PREFERREDLANG NVARCHAR2 (10) DEFAULT 'en_US' ,

    ( 
     AL_ID NUMBER (38)  NOT NULL , 
     APP_ID NUMBER (38)  NOT NULL , 
     PREF_ID NUMBER  NOT NULL , 
     ENT_ID NUMBER (38)  NOT NULL , 
     ENTPROP NVARCHAR2 (255)  NOT NULL , 
     ENTVALUE NVARCHAR2 (1000) , 
     ENTDATAXML XMLTYPE , 
     ENTDATABLOB BLOB 
    ) LOGGING

    ( 
        STORAGE ( 
            PCTINCREASE 0 
            MINEXTENTS 1 
            MAXEXTENTS UNLIMITED 
            FREELISTS 1 
            BUFFER_POOL DEFAULT

        RETENTION

        CACHE 
    )

     START_ID NUMBER (38) NOT NULL , 
     NEXT_ID NUMBER (38) , 
     MAX_ID NUMBER (38) NOT NULL , 
     AUX_START_ID NUMBER (38) DEFAULT 0 , 
     AUX_MAX_ID NUMBER (38) DEFAULT 0 
    ) LOGGING
;

CREATE TABLE SELECTED_FORM 
    ( 
     ID NUMBER (38) NOT NULL , 
     TID NVARCHAR2 (80)  NOT NULL , 
     FORMID NUMBER (19,4)  NOT NULL , 
     NAME NVARCHAR2 (512)  NOT NULL , 
     DESCRIPTION NVARCHAR2 (512) , 
     NAME2 NVARCHAR2 (256) , 
     NAME1 NVARCHAR2 (256) , 
     LVL NUMBER (10) DEFAULT 4  NOT NULL , 
     CATEGORY1 NVARCHAR2 (512) , 
     GROUP3 NVARCHAR2 (256),
     CREATION_TIMESTAMP TIMESTAMP ,
     RECIPNAME NVARCHAR2(256) 
    ) LOGGING 
;



ALTER TABLE SELECTED_FORM 
    ADD CONSTRAINT PK_SELECTEDFORM PRIMARY KEY ( TID, ID ) DEFERRABLE ;


CREATE TABLE SELECTED_INFO 
    ( 
     NAME NVARCHAR2 (512)  NOT NULL , 
     VALUE NVARCHAR2 (512)  NOT NULL , 
     INFOID NUMBER (38) NOT NULL , 
     TID NVARCHAR2 (256)  NOT NULL , 
     ID NUMBER (38) NOT NULL , 
     CREATION_TIMESTAMP TIMESTAMP 
    ) LOGGING 
;



ALTER TABLE SELECTED_INFO 
    ADD CONSTRAINT PK_SELECTED_INFO PRIMARY KEY ( INFOID ) ;


CREATE TABLE SELECTED_RECIP 
    ( 
     NAME NVARCHAR2 (512)  NOT NULL , 
     DESCRIPTION NVARCHAR2 (512) , 
     CCOUNT NUMBER (5) , 
     RECIPID NUMBER (38)  NOT NULL , 
     TID NVARCHAR2 (256)  NOT NULL , 
     ID NUMBER (19,4) NOT NULL ,  
     CREATION_TIMESTAMP TIMESTAMP 
    ) LOGGING
;

ALTER TABLE SELECTED_RECIP 
    ADD CONSTRAINT PK_SELECTED_RECIP PRIMARY KEY
    (
     RECIPID
    )
;


CREATE TABLE UCMFIELDS 
    ( 
     FIELDNAME NVARCHAR2 (30)  NOT NULL , 
     DISPLAYNAME NVARCHAR2 (30) , 
     JAVATYPE NVARCHAR2 (10) , 
     DESCRIPTION NVARCHAR2 (64) 
    ) LOGGING 
;



ALTER TABLE UCMFIELDS 
    ADD CONSTRAINT PK_UCMFIELDS PRIMARY KEY ( FIELDNAME ) ;


CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW DMKR_DISTRIBUTION AS SELECT  
        TRNS.JOB_ID AS JOB_ID, 
        TRNS.KEYID AS KEY_ID, 
        RCPS.RCPUNIQUE_ID AS RCPUNIQUE_ID,
        RCPS.BATCHNAME AS BATCHNAME, 
        RCPS.BATCHTYPE AS BATCHTYPE, 
        RCPS.RCPSTATUS AS RCPSTATUS, 
        RCPS.RCPOUTTYPE AS RCPOUTTYPE, 
        RCPS.RCPSTARTTIME AS RCPSTARTTIME, 
        RCPS.RCPENDTIME AS RCPENDTIME, 
        RCPS.RCPPAGECOUNT AS RCPPAGECOUNT, 
        RCPS.RCPSHEETCOUNT AS RCPSHEETCOUNT, 
        RCPS.ADR_NAME AS ADR_NAME, 
        RCPS.ADR_NAME2 AS ADR_NAME2, 
        RCPS.ADR_ADDRESS1 AS ADR_ADDRESS1, 
        RCPS.ADR_ADDRESS2 AS ADR_ADDRESS2, 
        RCPS.ADR_CITY AS ADR_CITY, 
        RCPS.ADR_STATE AS ADR_STATE, 
        RCPS.ADR_COUNTRY AS ADR_COUNTRY, 
        RCPS.ADR_POSTALCODE AS ADR_POSTALCODE, 
        RCPS.ADR_EMAIL AS ADR_EMAIL, 
        RCPS.ADR_ENCLOSURES AS ADR_ENCLOSURES, 
        RCPS.ADR_FAX AS ADR_FAX, 
        RCPS.ADR_PHONE AS ADR_PHONE, 
        RCPS.ADR_SELECTED AS ADR_SELECTED, 
        RCPS.ADR_ROLE AS ADR_ROLE, 
        RCPS.ADR_TYPE AS ADR_TYPE, 
        RCPS.ADR_LANGUAGE AS ADR_LANGUAGE, 
        RCPS.RCPERR_ID AS RCPERR_ID, 
        RCPS.RCBRCPNAME AS RCBRCPNAME,
        BCHS_RCPS.BCH_ID AS BCH_ID, 
        BCHS_RCPS.RCP_ID AS RCP_ID, 
        BCHS_RCPS.TRN_ID AS TRN_ID, 
        BCHS.BCH_ID AS BCH_ID1, 
        BCHS.BCHNAME AS BCHNAME, 
        BCHS.BCHSTATUS AS BCHSTATUS,
        PUBS.BCH_ID AS BCH_ID2, 
        PUBS.PUB_ID AS PUB_ID, 
        PUBS.PUBBEGINRCP_ID AS PUBBEGINRCP_ID, 
        PUBS.PUBENDRCP_ID AS PUBENDRCP_ID, 
        PUBS.PUBUNIQUE_ID AS PUBUNIQUE_ID, 
        PUBS.PUBNAME AS PUBNAME, 
        PUBS.PUBPRTTYPE AS PUBPRTTYPE, 
        PUBS.PUBSTATUS AS PUBSTATUS, 
        PUBS.PUBARCTITLE AS PUBARCTITLE, 
        PUBS.PUBARCSTATUS AS PUBARCSTATUS, 
        PUBS.PUBARCSTARTTIME AS PUBARCSTARTTIME, 
        PUBS.PUBARCENDTIME AS PUBARCENDTIME,
        PUBS.PUBOUTBLOB AS PUBOUTBLOB,
        PUBS.PUBMIMETYPE AS PUBMIMETYPE,
        PUBS.PUBPRTEXT AS PUBPRTEXT
    FROM 
        BCHS_RCPS
    JOIN BCHS ON BCHS.BCH_ID=BCHS_RCPS.BCH_ID 
    JOIN RCPS ON RCPS.RCP_ID=BCHS_RCPS.RCP_ID
    JOIN TRNS ON TRNS.TRN_ID=BCHS_RCPS.TRN_ID
    LEFT JOIN PUBS ON PUBS.BCH_ID=BCHS_RCPS.BCH_ID AND PUBS.PUBBEGINRCP_ID=BCHS_RCPS.RCP_ID AND 
    PUBS.PUBENDRCP_ID=BCHS_RCPS.RCP_ID
;

ALTER TABLE CATEGORY 
    ADD CONSTRAINT CATEGORY_MRL_REL1 FOREIGN KEY 
    ( 
     CONFIG
    ) 
    REFERENCES MRLCONFIG 
    ( 
     CONFIG
    )

CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER ATTACHMENTS_TRIGGER 
    BEFORE INSERT ON ATTACHMENTS REFERENCING 
    NEW AS NEW 
    FOR EACH ROW 
    BEGIN 
       SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.CREATION_TIMESTAMP FROM DUAL;
    END; 
/


CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER SELECTEDFORMTRGR 
    BEFORE INSERT ON SELECTED_FORM REFERENCING 
    FOR EACH ROW 
    BEGIN 
       SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.CREATION_TIMESTAMP FROM DUAL;
    END; 
/

    BEFORE INSERT ON SELECTED_INFO 
    FOR EACH ROW
    BEGIN 
       SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.CREATION_TIMESTAMP FROM DUAL;
    END; 
/


CREATE OR REPLACE TRIGGER addresseetrgr 
    BEFORE INSERT ON ADDRESSEE REFERENCING 
    FOR EACH ROW 
    BEGIN 
       SELECT TO_TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'GMT','YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF'),'YYYY.MM.DD HH24:MI:SS.FF') INTO :NEW.creation_timestamp FROM DUAL;

     END; 
/
